page1.title: Brand Babu
page1.description: Diamond Babu is a person who is obsessed with brands, he inherits the quality from his father who ensures even the matchbox used in his house is of reputed brand and dress code at a funeral is white and white, he molds his son like him.

page1.title: CoCo Kokila
page1.description: A woman gets caught up in a drug smuggling operation.

page1.title: NOTA
page1.description: An inexperienced bachelor is appointed chief minister when his corrupt father retires.

page1.title: W/O Ram
page1.description: A woman goes on a journey to find justice as she struggles in modern life, having to cope with the uncivility of patriarchal society and the misogynistic behaviour of others.

page1.title: U Turn
page1.description: When a flyover in the city becomes the hotbed of accidents, a young reporter decides to investigate the issue. Her quest for an answer would lead her into a web of intrigue, murder and mystery.

page2.title: Hello
page2.description: Although years have passed, a young man refuses to let go of the belief that he will be reunited with his soul mate.

page2.title: Srinivasa Kalyanam
page2.description: The movie deals with the importance of marriage and the traditional Indian values associated with it.

page2.title: Krishnarjuna Yuddham
page2.description: Two playboys who hail from different locales come face-to-face and are shocked to discover that they are look-a-likes.

page2.title: Goodachari
page2.description: Gopi, alias Arjun, is the son of an ex-RAW agent Raghuveer. Gopi wants to be an agent just like his father and uncle. But his uncle doesn't want him to be in that role. But some events change his life. A sleeper hit thriller!!

page2.title: Naa Peru Surya, Naa Illu India
page2.description: Surya is a short-tempered army soldier who almost loses his job due to an impulsive decision he takes. He will only be able to get the job-status back if he manages to get a no objection certificate from a famed psychologist.

page2.title: Mr. Homanand
page2.description: Homanand is a sincere man who works hard and finally pools enough money and buys a house. After a few days, he comes to know that there is a ghostly creature in the house which is trying to scare him off the property.

page3.title: RX 100
page3.description: The story revolves around a fierce young man and a drug addict Shiva who rides RX 100. He falls in love with Indhu, the daughter of a politician and the village head. Will Indhu reciprocate the love? *MATURE CONTENT*

page3.title: Chal Mohan Ranga
page3.description: Mohan and Megha enter into a thorny romance.

page3.title: Chalo
page3.description: A village called Tiruppuram is divided in half by the Tamil and Telugu people, and neither group is allowed to enter the other's perimeter.

page3.title: Tholi Prema
page3.description: Aditya and Varsha are irresistibly drawn to one another but their individual ideologies keep getting in the way of their romance.

page3.title: Desamudurs
page3.description: Two men cheat innocent people of their money to be able to lead a luxurious life but what happens when one of their such plans finds them in the clutches of a ghost?

page3.title: Kaala
page3.description: Kaala who runs away from Tirunelveli in his childhood, moves to Mumbai where he becomes a powerful don living in the slums of Dharavi.

page4.title: Officer
page4.description: Widower Shivaji Rao is a duty-minded, upright cop who comes with both ethics and guts.  He is assigned to head a Special Investigation Team to probe into the alleged misdemeanors of top cop Narayan Pasare.

page4.title: Pichiga Nachav
page4.description: Pichiga Nachav is about a fascinating guy who enjoys his life to the fullest. He takes it easy and is a happy go lucky kind of a person. But life takes a U -turn when he falls in love with a beautiful girl.

page4.title: Raju Gadu
page4.description: A thief tries to change his ways to win a woman's heart.

page4.title: Mahanati
page4.description: The life story of South Indian actress Savitri, who took the film industry by storm in the late '50s and '60s.

page4.title: Pizza 3
page4.description: The film tells the tale of a man who encounters paranormal activities in his new home. A sequel to Jithan (2005) and Telugu Dubbed Version of 2016 Tamil movie Jithan 2.

page4.title: Mr. Karthik
page4.description: The movie depicts the story of an aspiring wildlife photographer and his struggles in life. Telugu Dubbed Version of 2011 Tamil movie Mayakkam Enna.

page5.title: Dwaraka
page5.description: A thief (Vijay Deverakonda) contemplates changing his ways after he falls in love. A comedy-drama entertainer!!

page5.title: London Babulu
page5.description: The story follows the lives of two friends Gandhi and Pandu and how their desperation to earn money by working abroad leads them to make a series of wrong choices. A remake of the 2016 Tamil film Aandavan Kattalai.

page5.title: Juliet Lover Of Idiot
page5.description: Vara is an orphan, vagabond valet driver who has a massive pile-up of debt to pay. Julie is the quintessential rich girl he loves to stalk. But when their relationship goes south and he ends up embroiled in a comedy of errors, how will Vara cope?

page5.title: Bharat Ane Nenu
page5.description: To make good on a promise he made to his mother, a university graduate returns to India and becomes disillusioned by the government corruption he encounters. It is 4th highest-grossing Telugu movie of all time.

page5.title: Kirrak Party
page5.description: Krishna is a happy-go-lucky first-year engineering student with not a care in life. He falls in love with his senior Meera who’s a do-gooder and urges him to tap into the unseen side of him. A remake of the Kannada film Kirik Party (2016).

page5.title: Agnyaathavaasi
page5.description: The exiled heir to a billionaire masquerades as an employee at his father's company to find out who murdered his father. A romantic action movie!!

page6.title: Abhinetri
page6.description: Due to family pressure, a corporate man reluctantly marries a woman from the village, but in their new home, she abruptly assumes a different persona. A gothic horror comedy shot in Tamil, Telugu, and Hindi as Devi, Abhinetri, and Tutak Tutak Tutiya.

page6.title: Howrah Bridge
page6.description: Rahul Ravindran is obsessed with his childhood sweetheart Sweety. But as time passes by, he leaves his village and settles down in Kolkotta. One fine day, he decides to find his love and comes back to his village. But the unexpected happens...

page6.title: Kanam
page6.description: After an abortion, a woman's life takes an unexpected turn when she is visited by the fetus, who is now grown up and is visible to her. A bilingual horror thriller drama!!

page6.title: Hyderabad Love Story
page6.description: When Karthik and Bhagya Lakshmi are about to propose each other, Karthik’s ex-lover Vaishnavi enters the story.  A romantic drama!!

page6.title: Mercury
page6.description: Five friends, all affected in some way by a mercury poisoning incident are partying when a freak accident put them on a collision course with an entity that is in no mood to forgive their misgivings. A sound film which lacks dialogues!!

page6.title: Rangasthalam
page6.description: Chitti Babu, a hearing impaired boat skipper, becomes caught in the middle of a political feud in the village of Rangasthalam. A critically acclaimed action drama and 3rd highest grossing Telugu film of all time.

page7.title: Jandhyala Rasina Premakatha
page7.description: Different people from different facets of life contemplate on what love means to them and what their stance is on it. The movie charts the journey of how they deal with the concept of love in their lives. A romantic drama!!

page7.title: Marla Puli
page7.description: A suspense thriller which is based on a true story occurred in 1983.The movie is directed by D. Rama Krishna and featured Varun Sandesh, Posani Krishna Murali, and Veda Archana Sastry as lead characters.

page7.title: Anando Brahma
page7.description: A man who wants to sell his ancestral home hears rumors of it being haunted. Unwilling to sell the property at a throwaway price, he asks a team of four guys to spend a night in the house and prove that it isn't a ghost den. A super hit horror-comedy!!

page7.title: Jai Lava Kusa
page7.description: Jai Lava Kusa are triplets who get separated during their childhood because of small clashes.But their personalities are very different from each other.What happens when they accidentally meet? A blockbuster action-drama!!

page7.title: Chinni Chinni Asalu Nalo Regene
page7.description: The movie revolves around Gatta Manu who is truly in love with a girl’s voice over the phone oblivious of her identity. A romantic drama movie!!

page7.title: Raja The Great
page7.description: Raja is a blind man who’s trained to use his disability to his advantage. On the other hand, an honest police officer's efforts to bring a powerful crime lord to justice cost him his life and endanger his beloved daughter. An action-comedy-thriller!!

page8.title: Police Police
page8.description: Ranadheer is a sincere cop who tries to remove the wrongdoers, whereas Ravikanth is a corrupt police officer who has tie-ups with antisocial people. An action movie!!

page8.title: Vykuntapali
page8.description: Chandu, Kranthi, Michael are close friends and studies in the same college and movie get twist after entering a girl into their lives. A crime-comedy-action movie!!

page8.title: Yagam
page8.description: Danny is in love with Nandini, an air hostess, who gets killed in Bangkok. Danny then moves to Bangkok to avenge her death, but things get murkier as he unravels the mystery. An action movie!!

page8.title: Vengamamba
page8.description: A story of a famous first Telugu poetess Tarigonda Vengamamba, a famous devotee of Lord Venkateshwara in the tenure of 1750-830.

page8.title: Simha Putrudu
page8.description: A young man supports his father in opposing a local MLA, who often gives them trouble.Telugu Dubbed version of 2011 Tamil action masala film Venghai.

page8.title: Shock
page8.description: A married couple's life is disrupted when the husband is shot and implicated by two encounter specialists as a rebel. An action movie!!

page9.title: Maska
page9.description: A man wants to marry a girl for her money. But things get complicated when he falls in love with another girl, who has a secret past. A super hit action thriller!!

page9.title: Kotha Bangaru Lokam
page9.description: A wealthy father disapproves of his daughter's relationship with her middle-class school-mate.The film became one of the biggest blockbusters of the year in Telugu cinema.

page9.title: Kshemanga Velli Labhamga Randi
page9.description: Three families live in the same neighborhood and their husbands, spend half of their salary on the unnecessary items and their wives always find it impossible to make the ends meet.A remake of Tamil film Viralukketha Veekkam (1999).

page9.title: Yevade Subramanyam
page9.description: A corporate man sets out on a journey of self-discovery.Much of the filming took place at the Everest Base Camp, becoming the first Indian film to be shot at the location. A super hit movie!!

page9.title: Bommana Brothers Chandana Sisters
page9.description: Two brothers steal for a living while their parents encourage and protect them. While attempting to swindle two rich sisters whom they are wedded to, they eventually fall for them. A comedy entertainer!!

page9.title: Project Z
page9.description: A thriller story about how police work, struggle and fight to catch the real criminals.A Telugu Dubbed Version of 2017 Tamil movie Maayavan.

page10.title: Idi Naa Love Story
page10.description: Abhiram's sister sends him to meet her boyfriend's sister. When he arrives at the house, he meets a young woman and the two form a close bond.A remake of 2013 hit Kannada film, Simple Agi Ondh Love Story.

page10.title: Rogue
page10.description: When a heartbroken man swears off women, especially women named Anjali, fate intervenes.An out-and-out entertaining action drama!!

page10.title: Jai Simha
page10.description: Narasimha is a man on the run with his one-year-old son.He bumps into Gowri who seems to dislike him for some reason, despite being his childhood friend.A death row inmate Rami Reddy also seems to hold a grudge against Narasimha.

page10.title: Raju Gari Gadhi 2
page10.description: Rudra, a mentalist, offers assistance in tracking down a ghost that is haunting a resort.A remake of the Malayalam movie Pretham (2016).

page10.title: Dangal
page10.description: Dangal is an extraordinary true story based on the life of Mahavir Singh and his two daughters, Geeta and Babita Phogat. The film traces the inspirational journey of a father who trains his daughters to become a world-class wrestler.

page10.title: Jawaan
page10.description: Two childhood best friends - Jai and Keshav - grow up with completely opposite ideologies. Years later, the two best friends become arch rivals.An action thriller!!

page11.title: Touch Chesi Chudu
page11.description: A police officer struggles to maintain a balance between his personal and professional life.

page11.title: Okka Kshanam
page11.description: A young couple spy on their feuding, married neighbors, who seem to be living a parallel life.

page11.title: Premika
page11.description: Two youngsters, Krishna and Shruthi are in love with each other and live a happy life. The only problem, however, is that the village sarpanch believes that his brother is killed by Krishna. What happens next, forms the crux.

page11.title: Bhaagamathie
page11.description: The film revolves around a woman imprisoned in a haunted house while she is interrogated by law enforcers investigating a politician they suspect of corruption.

page11.title: Mahanubhavudu
page11.description: A man who is obsessed with cleanliness must come to terms with his behavior or risk losing the girl of his dreams.

page11.title: Guru
page11.description: A remake of 2016 Tamil film Irudhi Suttru. A professional and aggressive boxing coach, who is black-listed by the association, makes it a point to find that one girl who fits the bill to bring a gold medal to the nation.

page12.title: MCA - Middle Class Abbayi
page12.description: The family drama chronicles the life of a young man, played by Nani, hailing from a middle-class family, who is willing to do absolutely anything for his family.

page12.title: Angel
page12.description: A man is shocked when the antique idol that he is trying to smuggle out of the country suddenly comes to life.

page12.title: Dr. Chakravarthy
page12.description: Dr. Chakravarthy is a Telugu movie starring Sonia Mann and Richard Rishi in prominent roles. The movie also stars Lena Abhilash Kumar. It is a thriller drama directed by Sekhar Suri.

page12.title: Yagnam
page12.description: Seenu loves a factionist leader's daughter. On learning about their romance, her father tries to kill him, but Seenu decides to teach him a lesson and also end his enmity with a rival factionist.

page12.title: Vasu
page12.description: An aspiring musician runs a college canteen and a music school where he teaches music. His father despises this as he wants him to become an IPS officer; but realizes his dream when he wins an award on the day his lover is getting married.

page12.title: Vara Prasad And Potti Prasad
page12.description: Vara Prasad & Potti Prasad is an out and out comedy flick starring Srinivas Avasarala and Vijay Sai and has been directed by Satya Varanasi.

page13.title: 10th Class
page13.description: 10th Class is a 2006 Telugu Romance film directed by Chandu and produced by Venkata Shyam Prasad under SP Entertainments ltd. The film stars Bharath and Kadhal Saranya in the lead roles.

page13.title: Subbu
page13.description: A college student rescues a girl from an accident but her father mistakes him for the man who got her pregnant. The shame drives the student's family to take their lives. Years later, the young man falls for the sister of the girl he rescued.

page13.title: Stalin
page13.description: An ex-army officer aims to bring about a change in society by implementing a simple formula of extending unconditional help to those who are in need.

page13.title: Somberi
page13.description: Sombabu, the only son of well-to-do farmers, is a pampered guy and a wastrel. His laziness is the talk of the town.A team of three villains covets the land belonging to Sombabu's parents. They hatch a plan to get Sombabu out of the way.

page13.title: Shankar Dada Zindabad
page13.description: A goon falls for a girl who manages an old-age home, and she mistakes the goon for a professor. She seeks his help not knowing that the man who wants the old-age home demolished is his boss.

page13.title: Satyabhama
page13.description: Krishna is a sand sculptor in Goa. He meets Satyabhama, a tourist at a coffee shop and falls in love with her at the first sight.Then he realizes that she is suffering from Short Term Memory Loss.

page14.title: Rojulu Marayi
page14.description: A greedy landlord tries to create a rift between a father and a son. Enraged, the son decides to fight against the landlord and bring him to justice.

page14.title: Raju Bhai
page14.description: Raju, a local thug falls in love with Anjali, who gets him to reform and earn a livelihood in a more socially acceptable fashion.However, Raju gets caught in a police bust-up of a brothel.

page14.title: Raju Maharaju
page14.description: Two brothers are at loggerheads because of their conflicting personalities; the older one is reliable, while the younger one is reckless. The conflict escalates after the younger brother accidentally kills the father of his brother's girlfriend.

page14.title: Student
page14.description: A 2000 Telugu movie starring Nishanth, Milani, Rathi, Jayasudha, Suthivelu, Chalapathi Rao, Tanikella Bharani, Ali, M.S.Narayana. Directed by G.T.Prasad.

page14.title: Nuvvu Leka Nenu Lenu
page14.description: Two childhood friends have always shared bittersweet moments. When their parents ask them if they love each other, they deny any such feelings; jealousy creeps in when the boy's marriage is fixed to another girl.

page14.title: Ninne Premistha
page14.description: A young man meets with an accident and loses his eyesight; three months later he recovers and goes back to his job. He meets a lady who is very affectionate towards him; reason being that his eyes belonged to her deceased boyfriend.

page15.title: Neetho Cheppalani
page15.description: Balu and Aishwarya like each other. But due to shyness, they don't express their feelings. When Aishwarya is about to express her love, Balu tells her that he selected a girl named Ramya to date for six months as per his parents' decision.

page15.title: Nenu Meeku Telusa...?
page15.description: Aditya has a strange disorder. His memory keeps refreshing every night he sleeps, but he wakes up with a blank mind every day.He falls in a situation where he is accused of a murder. The rest of the story is all about how he rescues himself.

page15.title: Nee Manasu Naaku Telusu
page15.description: A boy and a girl fall for each other at first sight but lose each other in a crowd before they could talk. They both go to many colleges to find each other in vain. Eventually, the girl's father arranges her wedding with someone else.

page15.title: Orey Pandu
page15.description: Pandu is a man with no mental growth.He accidentally bumps into a girl called Priya.Pandu is given special powers by a self-abandoned ever-living baba.The rest of the story is all about how Pandu uses those powers to win the heart of Priya.

page15.title: Naa Girl Friend Baaga Rich
page15.description: A young man is in love with a girl who lives in Hong Kong; she invites him for a holiday with the family.His bag gets exchanged with another man's who is carrying the heads of seven men.

page15.title: Operation Duryodhana 2
page15.description: An announcement at the start of the movies says the incidents in the movie are not directly related to any real incidents or people. The announcement was mandatory but doesn't the story sound very very familiar?

page16.title: Muddula Koduku
page16.description: Venu, a good-hearted guy, has only one severe problem - a disfigurement on his face.The rest of the film is all about how he realizes that it's the inner beauty that matters, but not the looks. (Telugu Dubbed Version of Ponniyin Selvan 2005 Tamil film)

page16.title: Michael Madana Kamaraju
page16.description: Michael Madana Kamaraju is a 2008 Telugu comedy-drama film directed by Nidhi Prasad. It stars Srikanth, Charmy Kaur and Prabhu Deva in the lead roles.

page16.title: Kurkure
page16.description: Kurkure is a telugu Romance entertainment movie starring Duvvasi Mohan and Bhuvaneshwari.

page16.title: Jadoogadu
page16.description: Krishna comes to Hyderabad with the intention to earn money and settle well in life. Krishna falls in love with Parvathy who hails from Kerala.She wants to settle in Dubai and convinces Krishna for the same.

page16.title: Intelligent Idiots
page16.description: It's a story about 4 B.Tech. Final Year Students, doing crazy Illegal activities online.Apart from this, the porn mafia kidnaps 18 girls in the city, even the City Police failed to catch them up. A crime thriller!!

page16.title: Indian Beauty
page16.description: Indian culture interests Dave. So he decides to work on its culture. Swapna is also interested in Indian culture and hence decides to help Dave with his project. In the process of working both Swapna & Dave are attracted to each other.

page17.title: Ice Cream 2
page17.description: The film is a sequel to Ice Cream, directed by Ram Gopal Varma.A group of youngsters head to an abandoned factory, located on the outskirts of the city, to make a short film; however, the entire plan turns out to be a nightmare.

page17.title: Homam
page17.description: Members of a mafia gang start suspecting each other, wanting to know the identity of the traitor, when their gang leader is nearly arrested.

page17.title: Aalayam
page17.description: Rajayya lives with his several sons and grandsons and the extended family all stay with him because they love him.Rajayya, however, has one unsatisfied wish - his granddaughter Sarada has eloped 30 years back, and he wants to see her again.

page17.title: Kushi Kushiga
page17.description: A businessman sponsors for his step sister's education without her knowledge that he is her brother. A remake of the Malayalam film Chronic Bachelor.

page17.title: Bhajantrilu
page17.description: Bhajantrilu is a Telugu film, directed by the renowned comedian M. S. Narayana and produced by K. Devi Vara Prasad. Starring Sivaji, Ali, Brahmanandam and Mumaith Khan.

page17.title: Bangaru Konda
page17.description: A zamindar possesses a valuable diamond called Trinetra diamond, which is as precious as Kohinoor diamond. An international mafia don called Rakesh Pandey eyes the diamond. Chandu plays a trick and helps the police to catch Rakesh Pandey.

page18.title: Aatadista
page18.description: Jagan, the jobless son of an industrialist, Rajendra, falls in love with Sunanda, the daughter of Rajendra's rival Raghunath. When they plan to marry each other, their families' animosity increases.

page18.title: Aa Naluguru
page18.description: Rajendra is a man of principles and never goes against them. He is in a moral dilemma when he is forced to take a loan from his neighbor, as he needs money for the welfare of his children.

page18.title: B. Tech Babulu
page18.description: B.Tech Babulu is all about the story of four engineering students who randomly meet in college. Each individual has their own struggles.

page18.title: Shamantakamani
page18.description: The story of the film is based on an expensive car called Samantkamani which is owned by Krishna.One fine day, the car is stolen from a rich hot spot in Hyderabad and a corrupt cop is given the responsibility of nabbing the criminals.

page18.title: Spyder
page18.description: A surveillance expert who wants to help people comes across a foe who is the very definition of evil. Can he stop the man before he destroys everything?

page18.title: Jaya Janaki Nayaka
page18.description: Gagan is very much in love with Sweety aka Janaki, a sweet-natured girl, ever willing to lend a helping hand to those in need. But she ends up rejecting Gagan and later finds herself in a situation from which there seems no escape.

page19.title: Lanka
page19.description: Lanka is a well crafted Telugu sci-fi thriller movie starring Sai Ronak and Ena Saha in prominent roles.The basic plot of the film deals with Telepathy.

page19.title: Goutham Nanda
page19.description: A rich man's son want to know the emotions in real life which he is unaware of since his childhood and when that is going to happen there comes the real problem.

page19.title: Gunturodu
page19.description: A hot-headed young man (Manchu Manoj) draws the ire of a powerful criminal lawyer (Rajendra Prasad), not realizing that the lawyer is the brother of the girl (Pragya Jaiswal) he has fallen in love with.

page19.title: Nene Raju Nene Mantri
page19.description: Story of Radha Jogendra (Rana) and the love of his life, Radha (Kajal). His whole world revolves around her and he can go to any lengths to make her happy. But what happens when such profound love takes the shape of cavernous ambition?

page19.title: Ghazi
page19.description: In 1971, a submarine called the PNS Ghazi ventured into Indian waters with the ambition of destroying the INS Vikrant. What stopped them? The heroes aboard the Indian submarine S-21. It's the war you did not know about. A war-thriller!!

page19.title: Arjun Reddy
page19.description: A brilliant medical student starts down a self-destructive path after his girlfriend is forced to marry another man. *MATURE CONTENT*

page20.title: Baahubali 2
page20.description: When Shiva, the son of Bahubali, learns about his heritage, he begins to look for answers. His story is juxtaposed with past events that unfolded in the Mahishmati Kingdom.

page20.title: Thanu Nenu
page20.description: A romantic comedy about a boy (Santosh Sobhan) who hates America and NRIs. Mistakenly he falls in love with a girl (Avika Gor) who wants to go to America.

page20.title: Darsakudu
page20.description: Mahesh is an aspiring film director who always dreams of making a new age love story. Somehow, he gets a chance to direct a film and kick starts its shoot. He falls for a costume designer called Namratha.

page20.title: Andhhagadu
page20.description: A blind man falls in love with the doctor who has arranged his eye transplant. The operation, although successful, carries unexpected and haunting consequences.

page20.title: Ekkadiki Pothavu Chinnavada
page20.description: A man (Nikhil Siddharth) begins to suspect that his new love interest (Hebah Patel) is possessed by an evil spirit.

page20.title: Mantra 2
page20.description: A girl living with an old couple in their house as paying guest finds out that the old couple died years ago and the house where she lives is seized by police.

page21.title: Mass
page21.description: A local gangster trying to deal with a gung-ho police inspector develops feelings for his business partner.(Dubbed Version of 2015 Tamil Movie Maari)

page21.title: Pandavulu Pandavulu Tummeda
page21.description: Naidu s a tour guide in Thailand and is a father of three children. He meets his old flame in Thailand who is also a mother of two kids. Meanwhile, a gang is searching for Honey relentlessly.

page21.title: Vagabond
page21.description: Before India's independence during the 1940's, depicts the lives of poor carefree villagers who are lured to work in Tea plantation farms and how they are forced to live rest of their lives as slaves with no traces of hope and freedom.(Telugu Dubbed)

page21.title: Neevalle Neevalle
page21.description: The film revolves around the aftermath of a relationship between a careless man and a serious woman. Despite being in a relationship, the latter walks out on the former due to his antics with other women.(Telugu Dubbed)

page21.title: Ride
page21.description: A young unemployed man needs to have a bike for his job as a collection agent at a chit fund office. His bike gets stolen only to be seen riding by another guy who claims to have bought it from black market. They decide to use it as per their needs.

page21.title: Chennai Express
page21.description: What could have been a sad journey turns joyful for Rahul when he falls in love with a woman en route to submerging his grandfather's ashes.(Telugu Dubbed)

page22.title: Sukumarudu
page22.description: Sukumar who lives abroad comes back to this home town because of property and also there is a beautiful girl waiting to fall in love, hero faces difficulty from few family members and what follows is how he manages to win hearts(and property).

page22.title: Vetadu Ventadu
page22.description: A young man is in love with a girl but is too busy at the sandalwood plantations to pay her the needed attention. She forgives him many a times, but eventually leaves him as he is uncaring towards her.(Telugu Dubbed 2013 Tamil Movie Samar)

page22.title: Lajja
page22.description: An unhappy wife finds love outside of marriage, but can she also find peace?Lajja is a take on the famous Chalam novel Maidanam.

page22.title: Geethanjali
page22.description: Filmmakers are haunted by a woman who committed suicide.The movie was remade in Kannada as Kathe Chitrakathe Nirdeshana Puttanna.

page22.title: Eedo Rakam Aado Rakam
page22.description: Two friends get into hot water when one of them tries to cover the lies that made him more alluring to the woman he loves.The film is based on Punjabi Movie Carry On Jatta (2012).

page22.title: Bus Stop
page22.description: The movie revolves around the character Sreenu (Prince) who falls in love with Sailaja (Sri Divya). Sailaja parents do not accept their love and keep spying on her. An Adult Comedy!!

page23.title: Dronacharya
page23.description: A realtor who specializes in ancient buildings is lured into buying a property that is believed to be haunted. The deal turns out to be fatal as he is killed, but his brother vows to avenge his death.(Telugu Dubbed Version of 2010 Malayalam movie Drona)

page23.title: Chaarulatha
page23.description: Chaarulatha is a 2012 Indian horror film made in Kannada and Tamil.A deceased conjoined twin returns to haunt the surviving sister.(Telugu Dubbed Version)

page23.title: Aravind 2
page23.description: Aravind is on the run from some thugs and ends up in Goa. He meets a film director, who is impressed with his acting skills and offers him a role. Shooting begins in a forest, but the unit begins to be stalked by a violent serial killer.

page23.title: Avanthika
page23.description: Sreenu shifts to the same apartment where Avanthika, an innocent village girl was killed. What situations will Sreenu face there? A horror comedy!!

page23.title: Ninnu Kori
page23.description: Separated by circumstance, two lovers reconnect years later when one of them is happily married to another.

page23.title: Manyam Puli
page23.description: The movie narrates the story of Murugan, an ordinary man who lives in a village near forest area and his transformation from Murugan to Pulimurugan.How does Murugan become Pulimurugan?(Telugu Dubbed Version)

page24.title: Guruvaram
page24.description: Guruvaram movie is made on documentary of Lord Shirdi Sai Baba. In which, for the first time villian artist Late Rami Reddy playing a soft role of Sai Baba in this movie along with Sana in a supporting role.

page24.title: Pelliki Mundu Prema Katha
page24.description: 'Pelliki Mundu Prema Katha' is all about a guy who gets to meet his dream girl after his marriage. His trials with two women are discussed in the film.

page24.title: Pisachi 2
page24.description: Pisachi 2 starts with a mysterious search to find the truth which turns into an unknown revenge in a deep wood forest. After realizing the hidden truth, who will survive? (Telugu Dubbed Version of 2016 Kannada movie Danger Zone)

page24.title: Killing Veerappan
page24.description: A master strategist is appointed following Veerappan's unabashed spate of crimes and murders. The official puts in place Operation Cocoon, which involves setting up a network of spies and informers.(Telugu Dubbed Version)

page24.title: Bengal Tiger
page24.description: Bengal Tiger is the story of a man from Athreyapuram in Godavari district who comes on a mission to Hyderabad. The film shows the conflict between two intelligent men - Ravi Teja as the hero and Boman Irani in the role of the villain.

page24.title: Badri
page24.description: Badri (Pawan Kalyan) is an ad agency director whose parents are settled in the USA. He has a love called Vennela (Renu Desai), who is a close family friend of Badri's family. Their parents want these two to tie the knot.

page25.title: Nee Sukhame Ne Korukunna
page25.description: Madhu and Swapna tend to like each other. But another guy also falls in love with Swapna. Madhu gets a job in a company and a girl starts moving close with him. The news reaches Swapna and she misunderstands Madhu.

page25.title: Srinatha Kavi Sarvabhowmudu
page25.description: The film is cinematic of life of 15th century Telugu poet Srinatha. The film is also the last film of the evergreen star NTR.

page25.title: Kumari 21F
page25.description: Kumari 21F focuses on a romantic relationship between Siddhu, a chef and Kumari, a struggling model. Siddhu's friends doubt Kumari's character and she rejects his proposal, citing a lack of maturity.

page25.title: Dhruva
page25.description: Dhruva is a remake of the Tamil hit - Thani Oruvan. It tells the story of a police officer who is hell bent on arresting a rich, sly criminal.

page25.title: Gulabi
page25.description: Gulabi is an action-packed love story set in the backdrop of exporting girls to Dubai. It is inspired from a real incident that came in news dailies when police arrested few Dubai-based businessmen trying to export girls from Hyderabad.

page25.title: Talla Pellama
page25.description: A 1970 Telugu Movie starring NTR ,Shanti Kumari, Devika and Chandrakala The movie was remade as Bidaaii in Hindi with Jeetendra and Leela Chandravarkar.

page26.title: Bhakta Dhruva Markandeya
page26.description: A children's feature colour film with artists under 16 years age. This is an educative and entertaining film inspiring the tender hearts of children and portraying the greatness of devotion to elders.

page26.title: Jagadeka Veerudu Athiloka Sundari
page26.description: A man finds a ring that gives the bearer great power but the goddess to whom the ring belongs wants it back.

page26.title: Mahatma
page26.description: A local gangster who gets into trouble frequently with politicians and the police decides to participate in the elections.

page26.title: Rechipo
page26.description: Siva, a thief, falls in love with Krishnaveni when they bump into each other. When she learns that he is a thief, she is heartbroken but Siva comes to her rescue after she gets kidnapped.

page26.title: Ayyappa Swamy Mahimalu
page26.description: The movie deals with the devotees of Lord Ayyappa and talks about the victory of good over evil, where Lord Ayyappa showers his blessings upon his ardent devotees and helps them in their times of distress.

page26.title: Mister
page26.description: Mister follows the life of Chai, who lives in Spain with his family. In an accidental meeting, Chai meets Meera and falls in love with her. Chai comes down to India and meets Chandarmukhi, who falls in love with him.

page27.title: Lacchimdeviki O Lekkundi
page27.description: Devi works in a bank as cashier. Naveen works in the same bank at the help desk and likes her. Naveen wants to become rich in life and agrees to a gang’s plan to steal the data of unclaimed accounts. A comedy-thriller!!

page27.title: Yamudu 3
page27.description: An uncompromising police chief battles a criminal operation that deals in toxic waste. A Telugu dubbed version of Si3/Singam 3,2017 Tamil movie and sequel to Telugu dubbed version titled Yamudu II.

page27.title: Sadhyam
page27.description: A man lends his revolver to a woman who saves his life. Soon after, she sets out to exact revenge on all those responsible for her misery.

page27.title: Athidhi
page27.description: Athidi(Mahesh Babu) is falsely convicted for killing his adopted parents and goes to jail for 13 years and when he comes back he loves Amrita (Amrita Rao) unaware that she is the daughter of his adopted parents.

page27.title: Anukshanam
page27.description: Inspired by a real-life incident, the film is based on a serial killer who sends a wave of panic.As the police try to investigate a murder case and the news is splashed all over television channels and media, more murders take place.

page27.title: Don
page27.description: Don is a Telugu action - romance movie, directed by Lawrence Raghavendra. The cast of Don includes Nagarjuna Akkineni, Lawrence Raghavendra.

page28.title: Ganga Muni 3
page28.description: A Telugu Dubbed Version of Kanchana 2 2015 Tamil Movie.Employees of a TV channel set out to capture ghosts as a marketing tactic. They choose a dark, spooky house and create fake ghost effects.

page28.title: Heart Attack
page28.description: Varun is a hippie vagabond wandering in Spain. He never believes in relationships and he comes across Hayati, who arrived in Spain to meet her friend. In order to capture her attention, Varun pretends to suffer from a Heart Attack.

page28.title: Jump Jilani
page28.description: Two brothers do everything in their power to keep their grandfather's hotel open. A comedy entertainer!!

page28.title: Drushyam
page28.description: A respected, self-made man (Venkatesh Daggubati) must think fast to save his family after a crime is inadvertently committed. a remake of Jeethu Joseph's 2013 Malayalam film Drishyam.

page28.title: Karthikeya
page28.description: A medical student, Karthik (Nikhil) gets entangled in a conspiracy surrounding a famous temple in a village and how he unravels the secret behind the series of mysterious deaths in the village forms the crux of the story.

page28.title: Lion
page28.description: A man (Nandamuri Balakrishna) wakes up from a coma and becomes embroiled in a conspiracy meant to hide his true identity.

page29.title: Sri Ramadasu
page29.description: Based on the life story of the great devotee-musician Bhakta Ramadasu.

page29.title: Winner
page29.description: The story revolves around Ram, an individual who is separated from his father due to some conspiracy at the age of 5. After 20 years, Ram works as a journalist and meets Sitara and falls for her. She has a goal to be become an athlete.

page29.title: Khaidi No. 150
page29.description: A man (Chiranjeevi) on the wrong side of the law is moved by the plight of farmers to do the right thing.An official remake of the Tamil smash hit - Kaththi. Chiranjeevi's comeback to acting after 10 years in his 150th film.

page29.title: Gautamiputra Satakarni
page29.description: This movie chronicles the life of a South Indian ruler of the Satavahana Empire in South India in the 2nd century CE.The film is Nandamuri Balakrishna's 100th film.

page29.title: Pokiri
page29.description: A police officer goes under cover as a hit man, falls in love with an aerobics instructor and wages war on a mafia gang.

page29.title: Robot (Telugu)
page29.description: Rajnikanth performs a dual role, playing both the scientist Dr. Vaseegaran and the humanoid robot he creates, named Chitti, a look-alike of him. Despite his humanoid appearance, Chitti has superhuman strength, speed, and intelligence.

page30.title: Wish You Happy Breakup
page30.description: Aspiring filmmaker Naresh's (Udai Kiran) girlfriend Nitya (Swetaa Varma) breaks up with him because of a lack of clarity in his career. Dealing with the heartbreak isn't easy for him and he contemplates suicide. But things eventually change.

page30.title: Care of Footpath 2
page30.description: Care of Footpath 2 (Maanja) is an emotional suspense thriller about millions of juvenile delinquents living in the slums, the environment which fosters their behavior, and how society reacts.(Telugu Dubbed Version)

page30.title: Trivikraman
page30.description: The movie is directed by Kranthi Kumar C.H. and featured Ravi Babu and Gehna Vashisht as lead characters. A horror-comedy-thriller!!

page30.title: Nikki And Neeraj
page30.description: This is about a young and dynamic lover boy who falls in love with a rich and proud beautiful girl. Nikki is the name of the lover girl and Niraj is the name of the lover boy.

page30.title: Bhamane Satyabhamane (1996)
page30.description: A desperate father Madan, who, after a bitter divorce from Janaki ,just can't live away from their beautiful child who is now in the custody of his wife. So he disguises himself and joins Janaki's household as a maid servant Bhama Rukmini.

page30.title: Arya
page30.description: Arya falls in love with Geeta, who is in love with Ajay. Arya shows his love by bringing Geeta and Ajay together.

page31.title: Meeku Meere Maaku Meme
page31.description: Aditya (Tarun Shetty) falls for Priya (Avanthika Mishra), his junior in college and the soon get into a relationship. Then a series of fights follow and an eventual break up. Will they patch up? Or has the distance between them grown too much?

page31.title: Viyabari (Telugu Dubbed)
page31.description: A businessman who wants to be rich loses out on family and social life. He marries a girl who loves him only because she would prove profitable to his business. He realizes what he lost after the death of his mother.

page31.title: Vangaveeti
page31.description: The events leading up to the assassination of MLA Vangaveeti Mohana Ranga leads to political turmoil and gang warfare in Vijayawada.

page31.title: 24 (Telugu)
page31.description: A scientist invents a time machine, which leads to a bitter battle between his evil twin brother and his son.

page31.title: Siddhartha
page31.description:
The saga of a man called "Surya" whose raging violence is met with the innocent love of a girl to
transform him to "Siddhartha."

page31.title: Nannaku Prematho
page31.description: Abhiram's (NTR) world comes to a halt when he learns that his father Subramanyam (Rajendra Prasad) aka Ramesh Chandra Prasad's days to live are numbered. His father has a painful past and the last wish is revenge.

page32.title: M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story (Telugu)
page32.description: The untold story of Mahendra Singh Dhoni's journey from ticket collector to trophy collector - the world-cup-winning captain of the Indian Cricket Team.(Telugu Dubbed Version)

page32.title: Shankara
page32.description: A college student unwittingly takes part in a crime that changes the course of his life.

page32.title: Friend Request
page32.description: The story is about a Facebook account which is haunted by a ghost. It sends friend requests and entices unsuspecting people to meet, which results in deadly consequences.

page32.title: Gentleman (Telugu)
page32.description: While returning from London to Hyderabad, two women co-passengers develop friendship. Catherine narrates how she met her boyfriend Gowtham and Aishwarya, tells that she is engaged to a rising businessman Jay. Are Jay and Gowtham one person?

page32.title: Moksha
page32.description: Moksha is a pampered girl. Her father, single after her mother's death, dotes on her so much that he will not even accept her step into the kitchen. The only time she seems to step out of her flat as her neighbor Srinu observes is during the night.

page32.title: Mallanna
page32.description: A Telugu Dubbed Version of  a 2009 Tamil language neo-noir vigilante thriller film written and directed by Susi Ganesan.

page33.title: Abhinandana
page33.description: The story revolves around Rani (Shobhana), an aspiring dancer, who meets Raja (Karthik Muthuraman), an aspiring painter and singer. They fall in love with each other as their mutual love for art unfolds at an art institute/college.

page33.title: 100 Kotlu
page33.description: 100 Kotlu Telugu Comedy Movie starring, Baladitya, Saira Banu, Brahmanandam, Produced by Manjunatha Movies and Music composed by Vandematharam Srinivas. Directed by Ramana Martial.

page33.title: Baava
page33.description: History appears to be repeating itself when, just like his father, a young man falls for a woman whose family disapproves of him. However, with his father's help, he chooses to fight fate rather than accept it.

page33.title: Villain (Telugu Dubbed)
page33.description: A bandit leader kidnaps the wife of the policeman who killed his sister but later falls in love with her. A Telugu Dubbed Version of 2010 Raavanan Tamil Movie directed by Maniratnam.

page33.title: Target
page33.description: Target is a Telugu romance - thriller movie, directed by Ramesh Raja. The cast of Target includes Mumaith Khan,Shiva Balaji.

page33.title: The Myth (Telugu Dubbed)
page33.description: An archaeologist (Jackie Chan) finds adventure while searching for a gemstone and while dreaming he is a general to an emperor.

page34.title: Vareva
page34.description: Vaareva is a 2011 Indian Telugu language romance film written and directed by Kalyan Mantena . It stars Goutham, the son of famous comedienne Brahmanandam making a re-entry and newcomer Shambhavi in the lead roles.

page34.title: Simha
page34.description: Srimannarayana is a professor who cannot tolerate social injustice. Janaki, his student has a mysterious past and is harassed by a bunch of goons. The professor tries to unravel the mystery and figures how he is related to Simha.

page34.title: Sri
page34.description: A young man tries to save the girl he loves and her village from a cruel landlord.Sree is a 2005 Telugu film which stars Manoj Manchu, Tamannaah, and Mohan Babu.

page34.title: Ko Antey Koti
page34.description: Vamsi (Sharwa) is a small-time thief who gets into a transformation mode after going through a prison term and wants to reform himself as a good man. He is good at scaling tall buildings as a thief.

page34.title: Gudu Gudu Gunjam
page34.description: The film revolves around the story of a father who undergoes several situations in the process of getting his son married. A comedy entertainer!!

page34.title: Kabali (Telugu)
page34.description: An aged gangster tries to protect his family and his business from his enemies.

page35.title: Attarillu
page35.description: Randhir, Dayanand, and Krishnamurthy are three best friends. Dayanand, who is the son of a noted politician wants to stay a bachelor all his life. Upset with this, his father asks Randhir and Krishnamurthy to take him for a vacation.

page35.title: Chase
page35.description: Chase is a Telugu Action Entertainment movie filmed in the Detroit area.

page35.title: Jayeebhava
page35.description: Bhavani Shankar and Narasimha are two warring leaders in that town. Ram is the son of Bhavani Shankar. He falls in love with Anjali when he is abroad. After coming back to the town, they realize they belong to two warring groups.

page35.title: Em Pillo Em Pillado
page35.description: The story is about the rivalry between two villages so much so that they are thirsty for each other’s blood. However, one village head’s son (Tanish) ends up falling in love with the girl (pranitha) of the other village.

page35.title: Don Seenu
page35.description: This film portrays Seenu (Ravi Teja) who belongs to an ordinary kin and his admiration towards his idol Amitabh Bachchan. Ardent with one of his movies, Seenu desires to become Don in his life and endeavors hard to plan the process.

page35.title: Bumper Offer
page35.description: Sai completes his education and wastes his time. He refuses to marry her mother Ramanamma wanted to put some responsibility on him. Sai"s father Rao is a clerk with a real estate firm run by Surya Prakash.

page36.title: Nachav Alludu
page36.description: Tenali Ramakrishna generally dodges the marriage-brokering efforts of his uncle, by mouthing platitudes about his distaste for marriage. His uncle's dreams are fulfilled when he falls for an RJ called Deepa.

page36.title: Maa Nanna Chiranjeevi
page36.description: A rich man is reduced to destitution by his wife's investment schemes; he loves his son too much to give him away to his wife, who leaves him. He moves to the city to find jobs and provide for his son and tells him that he is an undercover officer.

page36.title: Ooha Chitram
page36.description: Vamsi Krishna wants to become a Software Engg but their parents wants to see him as a police officer then he  join for that job. Rest of the story is about how Kaveri Jha enters in his life?

page36.title: Sampangi
page36.description: Sampangi is a 2001 Telugu Drama film starring Deepak, Kanchi Kaoul, Sivaji Raja, Chandra Mohan. Directed by Sana Yadireddy Produced by Kalyana Venkatesh.

page36.title: Eega
page36.description: Its protagonist is Nani, who is in love with his neighbor Bindu. Nani is murdered by a wealthy businessman named Sudeep, who is attracted to Bindu and considers Nani a rival.  He reincarnates as a housefly and tries to protect Bindu while avenging his death.

page36.title: Preminchina Kothalo
page36.description: Preminchina Kothalo is a Telugu action - romance movie, directed by G Muraliappas. The cast of Preminchina Kothalo includes Navdeep,Mallika Kapoor.

page37.title: Ramadandu
page37.description: The story of this movie deals with issues like why our country is lagging behind in sports and why only cricket is a popular sport here when compared to other sports.

page37.title: Tenali Ramakrishna
page37.description: Tenali Ramakrishna is a 1956 Telugu, historical, biographical film, based on the life of Tenali Rama Krishna famous jester poet of 15th century, produced and directed by B. S. Ranga on Vikram Productions banner.

page37.title: Santosham
page37.description: A rich architect marries the girl he loves against her family's wishes and moves to New Zealand. They have a baby boy and the wife dies in an accident; her family invites him and the child to a wedding in India.

page37.title: Gandikota Rahasyam
page37.description: Gandikota Rahasyam is a Telugu language film released in 1969. N T Rama Rao in the lead role opposite Jayalalitha . It is period drama. It was produced by D.V.S.Productions and directed by B. Vittalacharya.

page37.title: Mental
page37.description: Mental is an action drama that talks about a police officer who is sincere and ruthless. When he faces off against a powerful goon, things go wrong. What happens next?

page37.title: Nayaki
page37.description: This movie is about Gayathri's soul from 1980s who has been killing people in a village. Entry into this village has been restricted by the Government since people keep missing. Watch this movie to find out why Gayathri has been haunting this village for the last 35 years.

page38.title: Bava Nachadu
page38.description: Ajay is an adman who has a definite idea about how his future wife should be. He gets married to a village belle Kamakshi , handpicked by his mom from her native town Kovvuru. After marriage, Kamakshi meets with a hairline fracture.

page38.title: Iddaram
page38.description: Ajay wakes up in a hospital with no memory of the past. One day, a girl expresses her love for him. Ajay falls in love with her and when he explains his condition, he is forced to find his past.Will he find the truth? Watch to find out.

page38.title: Puli Bebbuli
page38.description: A 1983 Tollywood film directed by K. S. R. Das. This film stars Krishnam Raju, Chiranjeevi, Jaya Prada and Raadhika in the lead roles.

page38.title: Preminche Rojullo
page38.description: Preminche Rojullo is a Telugu romance movie, directed by Vishwa Prasad. The cast of Preminche Rojullo includes Vijayanand,Kirti.

page38.title: Avatharudu
page38.description: A Telugu Dubbed Version of 2007 Tamil Movie Aalwar.A wealthy man learns of the horrible conditions in a hospital and goes under cover to try to improve conditions.

page38.title: Adugu
page38.description: The young, rich, foreign-returned Samarendra (Samarendra) is ready to inherit his father's companies and property. However, he's so out of touch with the ways of our land, he has to be taught even how to pray in a temple.

page39.title: Dollar Dreams
page39.description: The film focused on the lives of 7 young characters. Each of them with a dilemma of their own. About careers in IT and US study/job choices that they feel pressured to make. The movie is based on 1999 US immigration hype.

page39.title: Krishnam Vande Jagadgurum
page39.description: A boy is adopted by his grandfather after his parents are murdered. He grows up to be an actor to honor a promise to his dying grandfather that he would perform in a play in his native village. The performance leads him to his parents' murderers.

page39.title: Puli Veta
page39.description: Telugu Dubbed Version of Vettaikaaran (2009 film).Police-Ravi is a student aspiring to become a police officer, becomes hunted when he helps his friend out of trouble.The hunted becomes the Hunter to secure his future.

page39.title: Manamantha
page39.description: One World, Four Stories. Manamantha is a human drama with simple emotions and subtle sensibilities. It follows the journey of four people at different phases in their life: childhood, youth, and adulthood.

page39.title: Rangam (Blu - Ray)
page39.description: A Press Photographer helps a team of youths to win the election by mocking corrupt politicians in his newspaper, but later the plot moves quite differently. Telugu Dubbed Version of 2011 Tamil Movie Ko.

page39.title: Shakti (Bluray)
page39.description: Aishwarya(Ileana) is on a road trip without her father's permission. Unknown to her she has a diamond known as "jwalamukhi". Few bad guys from Egypt are after Aishwarya and the jwalamukhi as both of them are the key to destroying India.

page40.title: Singamalai
page40.description: Singamalai is the son of a retired head constable. His father gets Singamalai graduated in law and at the same time wants him to join the police department. A  Telugu Dubbed version of Tamil hit Marudhamalai.

page40.title: James Bond
page40.description: A man (Allari Naresh) considers flight after learning about his wife's (Sakshi Chaudhary) past criminal activities.

page40.title: Inkosaari
page40.description: A group of college students decide to reunite seven years after graduating and re-live their college days and do that one thing that they had always wanted to do while in college but could not.

page40.title: Goppinti Alludu
page40.description: Murali Manohar(Balayya) is the son of the industrialist SVR(SPB). He arrives India from Switzerland after finishing his graduation. SVR fixes a girl (Sadhika) for him and asks him to marry her. To get rid of that, Manohar escapes back to Switzerland.

page40.title: Love In Shopping Mall
page40.description: A Telugu dubbed version of Angadi Theru 2010 Tamil Movie.The story on the lives of a salesgirl and sales boy of a popular Saree store in Chennai.

page40.title: Nenu
page40.description: Exploring into the mind of a youth who is mentally and physically abused in his childhood, the film shows how he slowly turns into a psychopath who kills anyone who comes in the way of the girl for whom he has an obsessive love!

page41.title: Brahmashri Vishwamitra
page41.description: A musical drama directed by Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri, featuring Balakrishna.The story is based on the life of Vishvamitra who is one of the most venerated sages of ancient times in India.

page41.title: Satyam
page41.description: Satyam is an aspiring lyric writer who has a knack for inadvertently getting misunderstood by the two people he cares for the most—his father and his love interest Ankita. Because he and his father don't get along, Satyam leaves home and starts living with his friends.

page41.title: Allare Allari
page41.description: A woman avenges her husband's death by killing two of three murderers; she gets a life sentence for her crime. She asks her younger brother to promise her that he would educate his son well and get him married to her daughter.

page41.title: Aggiravva
page41.description: A 1981 Telugu movie starring NTR and Sridevi.

page41.title: Aa Okkati Adakku
page41.description: A young man believes in astrology than in hard work; the girl he is in love with insists that they get married. Her father agrees to the marriage under pressure, but on a condition that the groom has to earn a sum of one lakh rupees.

page41.title: Aggi Baratha
page41.description: A young warrior has his hands full when he is threatened by an evil general. At the same time, he must save the princess from the general's hands.

page42.title: A Aa E Ee
page42.description: A Aa E Ee (Athalo Aame Inthalo Eeme) is about Chandram, an honest man and a devoted husband to Kalyani. His life takes a turn when he discovers that Pregnant Kalyani is suffering from a rare disease and he has to get Rs. 8 lakh for treatment.

page42.title: Jaisurya (Telugu)
page42.description: A con-man based in Kancheepuram decides to save the district collector from a contract killer. Titled Rowdy Surya is a Telugu Dubbed Version of 2004 Tamil Movie Jaisurya.

page42.title: 4 Boys
page42.description: 4 Boys Telugu Full Movie. Starring Venki, Nandini Kapoor, Rami Reddy, Sashi Verma and Bhole among others. Director by Sashi Verma, Music composed by Bhole, Produced by Yousuf Khadri.

page42.title: Ranga The Donga
page42.description: Ranga (Srikanth) is a thief who lives in Stuart Nagar. He was raised by his grandmother (Sakuntala) in her house. He used to steal from corrupt police officers because they could not file a complaint for the theft of money from their own houses.

page42.title: Sankham
page42.description: A martial arts enthusiast meets a girl who likes the sport equally, and they fall for each other. They both desire to exhibit their skills but the girl is forced to return to her hometown, and the man decides to pursue her.

page42.title: Kothimooka
page42.description: The story begins with an ex-MLA who is a corrupt politician and his goal is to get his only son Ramana married to the daughter of a union minister. However, Ramana is a dud in studies and he is repeating the same degree course since few years.

page43.title: Pattabhi Shekam
page43.description: Pattabhishekam is a 1985 Telugu, romantic film produced by Nandamuri Harikrishna on Ramakrishna Cine Studios banner, directed by K. Raghavendra Rao.

page43.title: Panchakshari
page43.description: Possessed by Devi Maa, a blessed woman predicts her own death, leaving her shattered family to deal with a look-alike.

page43.title: Baahubali: The Beginning (Telugu)
page43.description: Amarendra Baahubali is the common man`s savior. The people of his town worship him like they worship god. His son, Shivudu unknowingly becomes their hero. His return to the village is the beginning of a fight against the evil.

page43.title: Gopi Gopika Godavari
page43.description: Gopika works as a doctor on a boat hospital that serves the neighboring villages in the Godavari. Gopi is an orchestra singer. Gopi and Gopika get to know each other through conversation over the cell phone and become good friends.

page43.title: Sneham Kosam
page43.description: A bride's mother is murdered and her father's friend and their servant goes to jail for the crime. Years later, the bride's sister comes home to find out that the servant's son is taking care of the house..

page43.title: Andamaina Manasulo
page43.description: Andamaina Manasulo is a Telugu romance movie, directed by R.P.Patnayak. The cast of Andamaina Manasulo includes Rajeev,Ramya.

page44.title: Ankusham
page44.description: Telugu Dubbed Version of a 2008 Tamil language film.Dr. Sandhya is kidnapped from her home by a gang and taken to another location, where she is questioned about her husband's whereabouts.

page44.title: Ummadi Kutumbam

page50.description: Ravi (Tarun) is an aimless youngster who falls in love with Swati (Arti Agarwal) at the first sight. But he does not get an opportunity to meet and talk to her because of her over protective ruffian brother (Subbaraju).

page50.description: A tough cop performs an undercover operation and identifies some nefarious activities in the seas around the coastal town.( Telugu Dubbed Version)

page51.description: Sivamani (Nagarjuna Akkineni) is an honest cop in Visakhapatnam (Vizag). He falls in love with Vasanta (Asin Thottumkal), who aspires to become a singer. Dattu (Prakash Raj) is a mafia don, whom Sivamani troubles a lot.

page51.title: Sevakudu
page51.description: Ramachandrayya (Nasser) is an honest cop who wants his son, Surya (Srikanth) to become an IPS officer. But Surya isn't interested. But one day Ramachandrayya gets killed and an enraged Surya goes about setting the system right in revenge.

page51.title: Seethaiah

page51.description: An honest cop is given the responsibility of making sure an accused terrorist gets to a court hearing. Suspecting a frame up, the cop picks three other officers to try to discover the truth. A remake of 2004 Hindi Movie Khakee.

page51.title: Satya Harishchandra 1965
page51.description: Satya Harishchandra is a Telugu mythological film, based on the story of Raja Harishchandra who was renowned for upholding truth under any circumstance. Mahatma Gandhi's life was very much influenced by Raja Satya Harishchandra stories.

page51.title: Sathyam I.P.S
page51.description: Telugu Dubbed Version of 2004 Malayalam Movie Sathyam.The story circles around Sanjeev Kumar who is awaiting his selection into the police force. But it was being delayed by the then Police commissioner who is backed up by his political allies.

page52.title: Sankarabharanam

page62.title: Lakshmi

page62.title: Kurradu
