page64.title: Grahanam
page64.description: Dr.Raghavram is a practicing physician in a small village.Another doctor and a nurse work along with him at the clinic.One day when he is on his rounds, he comes upon a quarrel between a patient and his mother.

page65.title: Gowri
page65.description: A remake of a Tamil film, Thirumalai.A chance meeting on New Year's Day leads a young mechanic to a romance, but the father of his new girlfriend is not pleased.

page65.title: Gorintaku
page65.description: A remake of the successful Kannada Movie Anna Thangi.It depicts the story of an elder brother's love and affection for a younger sister.

page65.title: Shri Vinayaka Vijayam
page65.description: Shri Vinayaka Vijayamu is a 1979 Telugu mythological film directed by Kamalakara Kameshwara Rao and produced by Jagarlamudi Radhakrishna Murthy under Jaganmatha Arts. The film stars Krishnam Raju, Rama Krishna, Vanisri, M. G. V.

page65.title: Sri Anjaneyam
page65.description: Sri Anjaneyam is a Telugu film directed and produced by Krishna Vamsi. It stars Arjun Sarja, Nitin, Charmme Kaur in the lead roles

page65.title: Jagadguru Adi Shankara
page65.description: The film traces the life of the 8th century Hindu philosopher Sri Jagadguru Adi Shankara (Kaushik), who propagated the doctrine of Advaita Vedanta across the sub-continent.

page65.title: Sri Mahalakshmi
page65.description: A remake of Malayalam film Chinthamani Kolacase.A criminal lawyer goes all out to free hardened criminals from the long arms of the law only to serve his own brand of justice.

page66.title: Sri Tirupati Venkateswara Kalyanam
page66.description: Sri Tirupati Venkateswara Kalyanam is a 1979 Telugu, Mythological film produced & directed by N. T. Rama Rao on his Ramakrishna Cine Studios banner.

page66.title: Srimadvirat Veerabrahmendra Swami Charitra
page66.description: Shrimad Virat Potuluri Veerabrahmendra Swamy Charitra is a film made in the honour of Ancient Indian Fore Teller Pothuluru Veerabrahmendra. The film shows the life - history of the great fore teller.

page66.title: Srisailam
page66.description: Srisailam is a 2009 Telugu Action drama starring Srihari, Sajitha.Director: K.S. Nageswara Rao Producer: T. Ramesh Naidu

page66.title: State Rowdy
page66.description: A 2007 Telugu Comedy Movie Cast: Sivaji, Mallika Kapoor, Madhu Shalini Director: S S Vikram Gandhi Producer: K Srinivasa, J V Uma Maheswara Rao Music: M M Srilekha Screenplay: S S Vikram Gandhi

page66.title: Stri
page66.description: Stri is a 1995 Telugu drama film. The film was written by Palagummi Padmaraju with screenplay and direction by K. S. Sethumadhavan. The film has garnered two National Film Awards

page66.title: Style (Telugu)
page66.description: After losing his legs in a car accident, a dancer becomes a mentor to a talented woman (Lawrence Raghavendra).This film was dubbed in Tamil with the title Lakshyam

page67.title: Subhapradam
page67.description: Subhapradam is a 2010 Indian Telugu-language film directed by veteran director K. Viswanath, starring Allari Naresh and Manjari Phadnis.

page67.title: Gharana Mogudu
page67.description: A rich businesswoman decides to marry a popular, hard-working employee to prevent him from exerting his influence on other employees and taking on the management.

page67.title: Geethanjali
page67.description: Prakash, who is diagnosed with terminal cancer and Geetanjali, an equally ill patient fall in love with each other. With just six months left to live, will their love-story have a happy ending?

page67.title: Ghajini (Telugu)
page67.description: A man, who loses his memory every 15 minutes, has photographs, notes, and tattoos to remind him to kill the man who brutally murdered his sweetheart. A Telugu Dubbed Version of Tamil 2005 movie.

page67.title: Evadi Gola Vaadidhi
page67.description: A young man falls in love with a girl while he is engaged to be married to a don's daughter. The don sends goons to kill his lover.

page67.title: Evaraina Epudaina
page67.description: Venkat (Varun Sandesh) is a carefree guy. He is a smart youngster who looks for people around him who are in love, then he blackmails them by threatening to tell their family of their love unless they pay him money for his silence.

page68.title: E (2006)
page68.description: Telugu Dubbed Version of 2006 Tamil Movie "E".E along with his friend Tony carries out small crimes to earn money. E brought up in tough conditions, grows up as a tough, fearless and emotionless guy.

page68.title: Dubai Seenu
page68.description: Seenu's aim in life is to fly to Dubai and earn tons of money, but gets himself into trouble when he gets duped by a broker in Mumbai.

page68.title: Doosukeltha 2013
page68.description: Chinna is a witty and smart journalist. While he is conducting a sting operation on Minister Dilleeswara Rao, he is beaten by his goons and admitted to a hospital, where he meets Dr. Alekhya and falls in love with her at first sight.

page68.title: Dongala Bandi
page68.description: Three thieves steal a king's treasure and hide it in a jungle. They then draw map revealing the location of the treasure and tear it into three pieces, each thief keeping one piece, but they soon part ways.

page68.title: Dil
page68.description: Seenu (Nithin) is a new admit at Maharaja College of Arts and Sciences. Nandini (Neha) goes to the same college. Seenu is from a middle-class family. She is the only daughter of Gowri Shankar (Prakash Raj), who is a land mafia don.

page68.title: Devullu
page68.description: Prashanth is a professional singer whose career is soaring. He marries Nirmala his hot core fan, who is also singing. After the marriage, Prasanth career falters, however, just as Nirmala's singing career begins to thrive.A 2000 Telugu, Supernatural film!!!

page69.title: David Billa
page69.description: An ordinary man from the slums enters an underworld gang and becomes the most feared underworld don. Telugu Dubbed Version of Billa 2 2012 Tamil Movie.

page69.title: Devdas (1953)
page69.description: Devadasu is a 1953 Indian bilingual romance film, directed by Vedantam Raghavaiah and produced by D. L. Narayana for Vinodha Pictures. Aluri Chakrapani wrote the script based on Sarat Chandra Chattopadhyay's novel, Devdas.

page69.title: Devanthakudu
page69.description: Sundar is a stage actor. He falls in love with Meenakshi daughter of a miserly rich man Bhadraiah who dislikes Sundar. Bhadraiah fixes his daughter’s marriage with an aged billionaire despite his wife's protests

page69.title: Desamuduru
page69.description: Bala Govind is a program director for a TV channel. His fights for justice regularly get him into trouble. During one of these incidents, he saves a person from goons while severely thrashing Murugan, son of the notorious smuggler Tambi Durai.

page69.title: Deepavali (2008)
page69.description: Deepavali is a Telugu drama movie, directed by . The cast of Deepavali includes Venu,Mega Nair.

page69.title: Dee
page69.description: A youngster gets a job with a mafia head and things take a dark turn when a man puts a hit out on his boss' sister.

page70.title: Deyyam
page70.description: The plot starts with a man returning home late night. He passes through the graveyard; on the way to home and he finds a ghost mistaken for a woman and follows her.

page70.title: Dasara Bullodu
page70.description: Two young women are in love with the same guy, but he has feelings for only one of them.

page70.title: Danger
page70.description: When friends runs into the forest after the police break up their party, they stumble upon a ghastly scene as they discover a man preparing to sacrifice a toddler for a black magic ritual.

page70.title: Daggaraga Dooranga
page70.description: Gowtham is an AD filmmaker and creates an "imaginary model" for one of his ad films. That model happens to be Meenakshi, whose engagement is canceled due to Gowtham’s sleazy ads.

page70.title: Chirutha
page70.description: A young man with a tragic past meets the daughter of a rich man and falls in love, while trying to avenge the death of his father.

page70.title: Chintamani
page70.description: Chintamani is a 1956 Telugu movie, directed by P. Ramakrishna Rao, starring Rama Rao, Bhanumati along with others.

page71.title: Chintakayala Ravi
page71.description: Chintakayala Ravi works in a bar as a head waiter. He has a soft spot for software engineers because he came to the US with the dream of becoming a software pro. Unavoidable circumstances prevented him from reaching that goal.

page71.title: Chhatrapati
page71.description: Displaced Sri Lankans in a Vizag port is ruled by a local rowdy. This is the story of Chatrapati Sivaji who overcomes this oppression and how he reunites with his long-lost mother and brother.

page71.title: Chantigadu
page71.description: A teenager begins his college studies along with a girl from the same village, the girl falls in love with him but he rejects her affection following a temple priest who cautioned him that if any man who marries that girl, would lose his mother.

page71.title: Bunny
page71.description: Story of the film deals with Polavaram project, which is an ambitious one. By having Polvaram project as main objective, the first half deals with love episodes of hero and second half deals with mama - allullu thread

page71.title: Brahmachari
page71.description: A Telugu Dubbed Version of Pammal K. Sambantham, a 2002 Tamil comedy film.A movie stuntman is against the principle of marriage until he meets a doctor, who he dislikes at first, but later falls for.

page71.title: Bodyguard (Telugu)
page71.description: Bodyguard is a remake of the Malayalam film directed by Siddique. It was remade in Tamil, Hindi and in Telugu. The film is directed by Gopichand Malineni and stars Venkatesh and Trisha.

page72.title: Bobbili Puli
page72.description: Bobbili Puli is a 1982 Telugu action-drama film starring N.T. Rama Rao and Sridevi in the lead roles. Kongara Jaggaiah, Kaikala Satyanarayana and Rao Gopal Rao played supporting roles

page72.title: Blade Babji
page72.description: Blade Babji (Allari Naresh) is a pickpocket who takes up the mission of earning 4 crores to rescue the slum dwellers in his area from a builder. He and his gang go to Vizag and rob a bank. And they hide the loot in a building under construction.

page72.title: Billa 2009
page72.description: A police inspector sends a gangster-lookalike to uncover the gang's secrets.A remake of the 2007 Tamil film of the same name.

page72.title: Bhookailas
page72.description: Bhookailas is a 1958 Telugu Mythological film, produced by A.V. Meiyappan under the banner AVM Productions and directed by K. Shankar. The story is based on the Sthala Purana of Gokarna Kshetram in Karnataka.

page72.title: Bhale Ramudu
page72.description: A 1984 Telugu movie starring Mohan Babu, Madhavi, Murali Mohan. among others. Directed by K S R Das. and produced by Mohan Babu.

page72.title: Bhairavi
page72.description: Bhairavi is a 2008 Telugu Movie starring Vijay Anand Abhinaya Sri Sira Bhanu.

page73.title: Bhageeratha
page73.description: Krishna Lanka is an island in Godari districts. The only way of commuting to that island is by boats. Lots of people die due to bad whether conditions while they travel.Krishna Lanka's President Bullebbai wants to have a bridge to that island.

page73.title: Bhadra
page73.description: A youth from a city falls in love with his friend's sister in a village. The village is marred by rivalry between two gangs; during an attack by the rival gang, the girl's family is killed except her. The youth tries to protect her with his life.

page73.title: Bathukamma(2008)
page73.description: Bathukamma is a 2008 Telugu Film Direction & Music Composed by T Prabhakar. Starring - Sindhu Tolani, Gorati Venkanna, Vijaya Bhaskar.

page73.title: Anjani Putrudu
page73.description: A 2009 drama featuring Nagendra Babu and Ramya Krishnan.Cast:Nagababu, Ramyakrishna, Prema, Sunil Krishna, Chandramohan, MS Narayana, Ramireddy, Costume Krishna,

page73.title: Bandipotu
page73.description: The king of Saptasena looks after his people with utmost care. He suddenly gets affected with paralysis and he has only one daughter. His brother in law Soorasenudu decides to make use of the opportunity to seize the kingdom by marrying the daughter.

page73.title: Baanam
page73.description: The story is set in the town of Ranasthali, in the year 1989. Bhagat Panigrahi is preparing to become a police officer. His father, a former Naxalite, returns after 20 years before giving up his fight for the society for the reasons only known to him.

page74.title: Subhakankshalu
page74.description: Two lovers belonging to different religions run away and get married. As a consequence, their families, who were once friends, end up becoming enemies.

page74.title: Baasha (Telugu)
page74.description: Rickshaw driver Manickam avoids violence at all costs; when his brother, who is a cop, gets in trouble with some goons, it triggers the revival of Manickam's old self.

page74.title: Ayyappa Deeksha
page74.description: Ayyappa Deeksha Starring Suman, Sivaji, Rami Reddy, Narasimha Raju, Lirisha, Director P.C. Satya Reddy, Music Composed by Prem.

page74.title: Avakai Biryani
page74.description: It is a coming of age story of two individuals from two completely different backgrounds and cultural upbringing. The only similarity between them is the fact that they both belong to the same picturesque, historic town of Devarakonda.

page74.title: Athili Sattibabu LKG
page74.description: Athili Sathibabu (Allari Naresh) is a stingy guy and a ruthless money lender charging high rate of interest at Rs. 10 at every one 100 on a daily interest rate. He gives preferences to money over relations and love.

page74.title: Aathma Balam
page74.description: Aathma Balam is a 1964 Telugu romantic thriller film, produced by V. B. Rajendra Prasad on Jagapathi Art Productions and directed by V. Madhusudhan Rao.

page75.title: Athadu
page75.description: A gunman for hire is framed for murder, and assumes a dead man's identity while hiding from the police.

page75.title: Appu Chesi Pappu Koodu
page75.description: The film deals with how the middle-class families are getting cheated in the hands of gullible people. A sequel to 1991 Telugu Comedy movie Appula Appa Rao.

page75.title: Anumanaspadam
page75.description: Having found the map to a lost treasure, a man and his insomniac friend assemble a team to seek it. The team members begin to disappear one by one, causing fear and distrust among those left behind.

page75.title: Swagatam
page75.description: Shailu is a married, ill-tempered businesswoman living in the US, trying to care for her mother and young nephew. KK, who with his young daughter opens a shop across the street from hers, helps her find a new perspective on her life. Shailu falls in love with KK.

page75.title: Swayamkrushi
page75.description: A cobbler raises his dead sister's son and an orphan as his own, later he marries his childhood love and becomes rich. But things take a turn when his dead sister's husband returns from prison to claim his son and the money.

page75.title: Sweet Heart
page75.description: Raju (Aakash) is an orphan and studying engineering with a helping nature. He is against love in the youth. He goes to the extent of separating the lovers. His classmate falls in love with him.This film reaffirms that love strives on nothing but Trust.

page76.title: Sye
page76.description: Prudhvi (Nithiin) and Shashank (Shashank) are the leaders of two warring student groups in a Hyderabad college. They are fond of rugby union game, and they sort things out between them by playing rugby to prove superiority.

page76.title: Tagore
page76.description: A remake of the 2002 Tamil film Ramanaa.The film is about a common man who decides to abolish corruption altogether in the society at various levels.

page76.title: Tata Birla Madhyalo Laila
page76.description: Two petty thieves Tata and Birla plan to kidnap Mahalaxmi, foster daughter of Gajapati, who is a big realtor. They manage to get some employment in Gajapati's house and Tata falls for Mahalaxmi.

page76.title: Tiladanam
page76.description: The story of a poor Brahmin who is forced to take alms from so-called lower castes and the impact it has on him and his family from those around him.

page76.title: Ullasamga Utsahamga
page76.description: A love story between childhood friend BALAJI and only friend Arvind. Which one should Dhana choose to spend his entire life with?

page76.title: Valliddari Vayasu Padahare
page76.description: It is a story about a boy and girl falling in love at the sweet and tender age of sixteen. The moment their parents come to know about it, as it is customary penchant with every parent, they make a big issue out of it.

page77.title: Vasantam
page77.description: Ashok and Julie are childhood friends. Ashok is a family member of Julie's family. They are pretty close and they believe that friendship is above love. They do not have any love feelings towards each other. Nandini and Ashok fall in love and get married.

page77.title: Veduka
page77.description: Harini is a fun loving girl who loves making teenage boys whomever she meets into bakras by fooling them. In the process, she rubs on the wrong side of a psycho. Srikar is a down to earth person who likes to lead a simple life though he is a son of a rich man.

page77.title: Veedokkade
page77.description: A Telugu Dubbed Version of 2009 Tamil Movie Ayan.The film's story revolves around Deva, a youngster whose mother wants him to become a government official. He, on the other hand, works for a smuggling group run by Arumuga Dass.

page77.title: Victory (2008)
page77.description: Nitin plays the role of a vibrant, energetic youngster who is also a well responsible boy. The film throws light on the dreaded Land Mafia. Nitin who fight against them at last wins over them.

page77.title: Vijay IPS
page77.description: Vijay IPS is a Telugu action - drama movie, directed by K.Hanumantha Reddy. The cast of Vijay IPS includes Sumanth,Kaikala Satyanarayana.

page77.title: Vijetha
page77.description: The movie is a remake of Hindi movie Saaheb starring Anil Kapoor and Amrita Singh, which is a remake of the Bengali film of the same name.

page78.title: Yamudiki Mogudu
page78.description: This is a story of reincarnation and karmic justice.This film was remade in Tamil as Athisaya Piravi with Rajinikanth.

page78.title: Yogi
page78.description: Yogi goes to the city and must battle the mafia after he kills a thug in a fight, but soon a tragedy will strike. A remake of the 2005 Kannada film Jogi.

page78.title: Yuganiki Okkadu
page78.description: Anita leads a military group to an unexplored island to find a missing archaeologist and to know about a Chola Prince who went into hiding. They face unexpected adventures. Telugu Dubbed version of 2010 Tamil movie Ayirathil Oruvan.

page78.title: Yuvasena
page78.description: Four angry engineering students, fed up with the corruption in society, take the law into their own hands and form a secretive group called 4 The People whose purpose is to take out corrupt officials.

page78.title: Yuvatha
page78.description: Babu, an orphan brought up by his uncle and aunt believes that they swindled his property. Once when his uncle chides him, he leaves home for Hyderabad to stay with his friends, whom he trusts.Babu meets Baby and they become good friends.

page78.title: Anukokunda Oka Roju
page78.description: Sahasra is a chorus singer struggling to make a career in playback singing. One night she attends a wild party at the behest of her friend. The next day, life seems as usual for Sahasra. Only she is oblivious of one small detail: The next day is actually the day after.

page79.title: Annavaram
page79.description: Varam's brother, Annavaram, dotes on her. They visit a village, and Annavaram arranges the marriage of his sister to a guy from Hyderabad, but goons in the city harass Varam and her husband.A remake of Tamil blockbuster film Thirupaachi.

page79.title: Anji
page79.description: A young woman finds intrigue while investigating a mystery in India.The Aatmalingam of the Himalayas possesses enormous divine powers. Those who drink the holy water of Akasa Ganga become younger for eternity and gain supernatural powers.

page79.title: Anjaneyulu
page79.description: A news reporter joins a gang incognito to expose corrupt politicians as well as find out who killed his parents.

page79.title: Andhrudu
page79.description: Surendra is an honest and hot-blooded cop. Archana is the daughter of police commissioner. They meet accidentally and their relationship blossoms into love. Archana's father is of Bihar origin.

page79.title: Andarivaadu
page79.description: Govinda Rajulu is a worker who drinks a lot and lives a care-free life. His son Siddartha, on the other hand, is a popular TV show host and is a more disciplined man — the opposite of his dad. The son gets his father married to Shanti to sober him.

page79.title: Ammoru
page79.description: A goddess protects a girl from a woman who wants revenge for her son's incarceration.

page80.title: Amma Cheppindi
page80.description: Bose, a mentally underdeveloped youngster. His family includes his father, who is a scientist in a rocket center, his mother, who dotes on him and his academically bright brother. Bose is considered to be dumb in the residential township and he is looked down upon.

page80.title: Amara Deepam (1977)
page80.description: Amara Deepam is a 1977 Telugu drama film directed by K. Raghavendra Rao. The film stars Krishnam Raju, Jayasudha and Murali Mohan in the lead roles.

page80.title: Allari Pidugu
page80.description: Major Charkavarthy , has two sons Ranjit and Giri. Giri is the younger one, who is the village guy and in love with his cousin Subbalakshmi. Ranjit turns into an ACP and meets his match Swati.

page80.title: Allari Priyudu
page80.description: A romantic drama directed by K. Raghavendra Rao, featuring Rajasekhar and Ramya Krishna.

page80.title: Akbar Salim Anarkali
page80.description: Akbar Salim Anarkali is a 1979 Telugu, Historical film produced & directed by N. T. Rama Rao on his Ramakrishna Cine Studios banner. Starring N. T. Rama Rao, Nandamuri Balakrishna, Deepa in the lead roles and music composed by C. Ramchandra.

page80.title: Aadivaram Aadavallaku Selavu
page80.description: Examining how women face society by stepping out of their homes as breadwinners, including a look at how much moral support they receive from their husbands.

page81.title: Aavida Maa Aavide
page81.description: A comical drama directed by Satyanarayana E.V.V., featuring Jagapathi Babu.It was loosely based on the 1963 movie Move Over, Darling.

page81.title: Aa Intlo
page81.description: Pavan(Chinna), and Pallavi (Mayuri) live happily along with their two kids. Their happy life is interrupted when Pallavi is affected with a serious health problem. A horror film!!

page81.title: 7G Brundhavan Colony
page81.description: An underachiever falls in love with a girl who has just moved into his neighborhood. He goes to extremes to express his love for her, but she keeps rejecting his advances. A Telugu Dubbed Version of 2004 Tamil Movie 7/G Rainbow Colony.

A man elopes with his childhood sweetheart, but soon fate separates them. The woman finds herself with a Communist guerrilla group and the man lands up at the house of a journalist, both thinking that the other is no more.

page81.title: Chanakya Chandragupta
page81.description: Chanakya Chandragupta is a 1977 Telugu Historical film produced & directed by N. T. Rama Rao on his Ramakrishna Cine Studios banner.

page81.title: Chanda Sasanudu
page81.description: A 1983 Telugu movie starring NTR, Sharada, Radha

page82.title: Kondaveeti Donga
page82.description: A man returns to his village and sees his people made to suffer by vandals; he decides to help them. Soon, he assumes the role of a local folk hero and sets out to exact punishment on the criminals.

page82.title: Bruce Lee - The Fighter
page82.description: A stuntman is mistaken for a police officer by an idealistic woman and begins fighting crime on behalf of the police.

page82.title: Ananda Bhairavi
page82.description: A dance teacher runs into trouble when he protests against society, which doesn't allow girls to perform Kuchipudi.

page82.title: Vivaha Bandham
page82.description: A 1964 Telugu Movie starring N.T. Rama Rao, Bhanumathi.

page82.title: Viyyalavari Kayyalu
page82.description: Vamshi (Uday Kiran) is a hair stylist who falls in love with Nandini (Neha Jhulka), sister of Bhoopathi Rayudu (Sri Hari), a good-hearted factionist. Vamshi and Nandini decide to get married only with the consent of their elders.

page82.title: Salute
page82.description: A Telugu Version of Satyam 2008 Tamil Movie.Sathyam, an assistant police commissioner, fights crime in his own way.

page83.title: Raana
page83.description: Raana is a Telugu drama movie, directed by Bharathiraja. The cast of Raana includes Arjun Sarja,Kajal Aggarwal. Telugu Dubbed Version of Bommalattam Tamil 2008 film.

page83.title: Prayanam
page83.description: A boy meets a girl in an airport and falls in love with her, but he has only 2 hours to convince her.

page83.title: Pallakilo Pellikuturu
page83.description: Pallakilo Pelli Kuturu is an Family Romance based movie. In which, Rani (Rathi) is a beautiful village belle raised by her rich grandparents. Her grandparents are so possessive about her that they never even allow her out of their house to attend school.

page83.title: Ninne Pelladata
page83.description: A woman comes to a big city to attend training and ends up falling in love with a man, whose family approves of her. But just before their marriage, her parents forcibly take her away, to get her married to someone else.

page83.title: Mallepuvvu
page83.description: Mallepuvu is a 2008 Tollywood Indian feature film directed by V. Samudra. The film has Bhumika and Muralikrishna who debuts in the lead role, supported by Suman Setty, RK, Sukumar, and Kovai Sarala.

page83.title: Kalisundam Raa
page83.description: Raghaviah and Ram Mohan Rao are brothers-in-law. But Ram Mohan Rao is at loggerhead with Raghavaiah because of a family feud. Raghavaiah is nearing his 60's and it's time for his Shastipoorti ceremony. It's time for gathering, folks!

page84.title: Bhayya
page84.description: A young man is granted conditional bail, which requires him to go to the Trichy police station. On his way there, he falls for a beautiful girl. When the girl lands up in trouble, he finds himself facing the wrath of powerful politicians.

page84.title: Apadamokkulavadu
page84.description: Apadamokkulavadu is a Telugu drama movie, directed by Posani Krishna Murali. The cast of Apadamokkulavadu includes Nagendra Babu,Asmitha.

page84.title: Swarabhishekam
page84.description: Srirangam Brothers - Srinivasachari and Ranga are versatile Carnatic musicians. Srinivasachari is happily married but has no children. Ranga is a widower with two children.

page84.title: Ramudu Bheemudu
page84.description: N.T. Rama Rao played the dual role as "Ramudu" and "Bheemudu". It was remade into Tamil as Enga Veettu Pillai (1965) With M. G. R, into Hindi as Ram Aur Shyam (1967) starring Dilip Kumar.

page84.title: Major Chandrakanth (1993)
page84.description: A drama directed by K. Raghavendra Rao, featuring Taraka Rama Rao Nandamuri.This film is perhaps a last glimpse in N. T. Rama Rao's long film career.

page84.title: Palnati Yuddham
page84.description: Brahmayudu, the wily minister of the kingdom of Palnadu, opens the doors of the Chenna Keshava temple to people of all castes, which leads to a revolt from the military instigated by Nagamma, the royal matriarch.

page85.title: Mahamantri Timmarusu (1962)
page85.description: Hamvira accuses Timmarusu, the prime minister in Krishnadevaraya's court, of being the main culprit behind the attack on Krishnadevaraya while creating differences between them.

page85.title: Bindaas (2010)
page85.description: Mahendra Naidu and Seshadri Naidu are faction rivals frequently fighting each other. Ajay, a carefree lad with a large heart and tough guts is alienated from the family of Mahendra Naidu because of his father. He is in love with Girija.

page85.title: Dalapathi
page85.description: Surya (Rajnikanth) is an orphan raised in a slum. He finds a friend in the local Godfather (Mamooty). They rule the town and forms a parallel government.

page106.description: A greedy man starts a marriage bureau assuring that he can get a beggar married too and gives one-year marriage guarantee to his clients. A client, who is a misogamist, wants to get married but it is tough to find a suitable match for her.

page106.title: Saradaga Ammayitho
page106.description: The hero is an incurable romantic.His strategy clicks every time he wants to floor a girl as he can easily scan and detect what their weakness is. But the challenge arises when he meets the girl who proves a tough nut to crack for him.

page106.title: Potugadu
page106.description: The only competition Govind (Manoj) perhaps has is the eel. He falls in love - not once, but several times - and manages to survive like the slithering creature even out of the water. A remake of the Kannada film Govindaya Namaha.

page106.title: Ongole Githa
page106.description: White enters the Chilli market yard in Ongole at the age of 12. Adikeshava is the chairman of that Chilli yard. White comes to know of Adikeshava's real character and asks him to arrange a marriage with his daughter.

page107.title: Attarintiki Daredi
page107.description: The film focuses on Gautham Nanda, a business heir who acts as a driver in his estranged aunt Sunanda's house to mend her strained relationship with his grandfather Raghunandan who expelled her for marrying against his wishes years before.

page107.title: Dhenikaina Ready
page107.description: The story deals with Veera Narasimha Naidu a faction leader in Kurnool who raised his sister Saraswati with Love and Affection to make her forget the loss of their Mother. During the marriage time, she eloped with Basha, which led the death of Naidu's Father.

page107.title: Doosukeltha
page107.description: Chinna is a witty and smart journalist. While he is conducting a sting operation on Minister Dilleeswara Rao, he is beaten by his goons and admitted to a hospital, where he meets Dr. Alekhya and falls in love with her at first sight.

page107.title: Balupu
page107.description: Ravi is a recovery agent for a bank when comes across of con team of Shruti and her uncle Crazy Mohan he decides to teach them a lesson. But in the process, he and Shruti fall for each other. An action comedy blockbuster!!

page107.title: Telugabbai
page107.description: Two childhood friends living with their parents in Malaysia get involved in a love triangle involving a model.

page107.title: Prematho Nuvvu Vastavani
page107.description: Prematho Nuvvu Vastavani is a Telugu comedy - romance movie, directed by Thota Krishna. The cast of Prematho Nuvvu Vastavani includes Krishnudu,Archana.

page108.title: Sahasam
page108.description: Gautham Varma, an A.T.M security guard, goes on a treasure hunt for the diamonds hidden by his grandfather in the Hinglaj temple during the time of the India - Pakistan partition.

page108.title: Kevvu Keka
page108.description: Butchi Raju is a salesman and he stays with his uncle, magician Appa Rao. He falls in love with Maha Lakshmi, but her father Subba Rao does not approve their alliance as Raju is not a rich guy.In a bid to win her hand, he sets out to Bangkok to earn money.

page108.title: Ala Modalaindi
page108.description: On the day of his girlfriend's marriage, Gautam gets kidnapped by an unknown criminal. Bored on the way to the kidnapper's den, Gautam is forced to narrate his cute love story which is filled with loads of twists and turns.

page108.title: Shadow
page108.description: Raja Ram (Venkatesh) is the son of Raghuram (Naga Babu). Raghuram is Associate in Nursing, as investigatory journalist in a United Nations agency. He infiltrates the criminal organization of Nana Bhai (Aditya Pancholi) and earns his trust.

page108.title: Jai Bolo Telangana
page108.description: Jai Bolo Telangana is a 2011 Telugu historical drama film based on the Telangana Movement. It was directed by N.Shankar and the lead character was played by Sandeep Singh.

page108.title: Dasa Thirigindi
page108.description: Dasa Thirigindi is a Telugu thriller movie, directed by Satti Srinivasa Reddy. The cast of Dasa Thirigindi includes Shivaji,Sada.

page109.title: Gunde Jaari Gallanthayyinde
page109.description: Nitin becomes infatuated with a girl and gets her phone number from a friend. After many conversations on the phone, he falls in love without realizing he isn't speaking to the same girl.

page109.title: Prema Katha Chitram
page109.description: Three friends and a stranger go to a house and plan to commit suicide. But later they realize the house is haunted.An unexpected love story!!

page109.title: Mr. Pellikoduku
page109.description: Mr. Pellikoduku is the official remake of Bollywood rom-com Tanu weds Manu.When a young man's proposal is rejected, he redoubles his efforts to win the young woman's love.

page109.title: Iddarammayilatho
page109.description: A girl meets a young rockstar, whose past she comes to know from the diary of his girlfriend. However, the biggest truth of his past and his love is yet to be found, before her fiance plays any trick.

page109.title: Greeku Veerudu
page109.description: An overconfident businessman's journey of realizing the importance of family and turning from a stud to falling in love.

page109.title: Chaatam
page109.description: Gowri Shankar is a circle inspector and is known as a heavy corrupt police officer. Rangarao is his assistant and his daughter Sindhu is an aerobics, teacher. Once, two sons of a big industrialist kill two girls for not accepting their love by pouring acid on them.

page110.title: Orange
page110.description: A man, who doesn't believe that love can last a lifetime, pursues an exuberant romantic, but their clashing ideologies keep them apart.

page110.title: Dookudu
page110.description: Dookudu is about an honest police officer (Mahesh Babu) fighting a mafia gang and how he travels to Turkey in search of mafia leader, Prakash Raj. However, he discovers that his senior officer, Najar is hand-in-glove with the mafia.

page110.title: Dhada
page110.description: An Indian engineering student in the U.S. gets in trouble with local gangsters and must resolve his problems to return to his lady-love in India.

page110.title: Chapter 6
page110.description: The story begins with Bharath and Shilpa who have the initial hide and seek games and in no time, they fall in love. They also get intimate and Shilpa becomes pregnant but she is scared to talk about marriage since her father is the police commissioner.

page110.title: Nandeeswarudu
page110.description: A man lands up in jail after a series of incidents. Frustrated with the way his life is going, he decides to redeem himself and fight for the rights of the oppressed.

page110.title: Mr.Perfect
page110.description: A modern-minded software expert who refuses to compromise on his values becomes engaged to a young woman who is both conservative and traditional in her ways.

page111.title: Aha Naa Pellanta
page111.description: Subrahmanyam is an intelligent, hardworking software engineer. He lives with his uncle and spends most of his time with his girlfriend Madhu and his friend Balraj. After getting drunk heavily one night, he wakes up with another girl, Sanjana.

page111.title: 100 Percent
page111.description: Balu is a brilliant student and always tops his class. Maha Lakshmi comes from the village and stays in Balu's house to do her graduation in the same college. The rest of the story is all about how they realize that they are made for each other.

page111.title: Mirapakai
page111.description: Rishi sends to Hyderabad and join in a college as a Hindi lecturer as a part of an undercover operation. He fall in love with her student Vinamra. Rishi has to extract information about Kittu from Vaishali, another student.

page111.title: Sarocharu
page111.description: After a chance encounter with a man in Italy, a female student's infatuation leads to unforeseen consequences.Directed by Parasuram featuring Ravi Teja, Nara Rohith, Kajal Agarwal and Richa Gangopadhyay in leading roles.

page111.title: Madatha Kaja
page111.description: A comic account of a police informer who comes across two dangerous criminal dons whom he wishes to bring to justice.

page111.title: Lovely
page111.description: Akash and Kittu are friends. Lovely and Lalli are friends. Kittu and Lalli become facebook friends with celebrity profile photos. When they are about to meet in real, Akash and Lovely go to the meeting pretending to be Kittu and Lalli respectively.

page112.title: Gundello Godari
page112.description: Gundello Godari is about a newlywed couple who are forced to battle it out against a devastating flood of the River Godavari. They lose all hope of survival, so they decide to narrate the darkest moments of their lives to each other.

page112.title: Devaraya
page112.description: Dorababu lives in a village in Godavari district and he has a gang of friends.His daily life is all about cards, drinks, women and has a carefree attitude. He comes across Swapna who comes new to the village and due to certain incidents she falls in love with him.

page112.title: Mirchi
page112.description: A man returns to his country in order, ostensibly, to reform his girlfriend's violent family, but he seems to have a strange connection and a rather dark past.

page112.title: Adhurs
page112.description: Twin brothers are separated at birth; one is raised by their mother, while the other by a priest's family. They are unaware of each other's existence until one of them is abducted by criminals because of a misunderstanding.

page112.title: Oye
page112.description: Uday is a rich kid who becomes chairman of a company following the death of his father. He believes in the adage of life is short and carpe diem. At New Year's Party 2007, he spies on a girl called Sandhya in a salwar-kameez, writing a diary at the pub.

page112.title: Seethamma Vakitlo Sirimalle Chettu
page112.description: Peddhodu and Chinnodu are two brothers from a small village. Peddhodu doesnt like his uncle's family, who often take this family and their traditions for granted. One day, his parents inform him that his sister is going to be engaged to a person suggested by that uncle family. This leads to a huge conflict between the two brothers.

page113.title: Nenu Naa Raakshasi
page113.description: Abhimanyu (Rana Daggubati) is a professional assassin who kills local gangsters for money. He rapidly falls in love with Meenakshi (Ileana D'Cruz), after seeing her working in a cafeteria.

page113.title: Koncham Ishtam Koncham Kastam
page113.description: Siddhu always wears a smile on his face but he has sad past. Geeta joins his college. Both fall in love and are ready to get married. But Geeta's father refuses their love unless Siddhu tackle his Past problem.

page113.title: Shirdi Sai
page113.description: Shirdi Sai appears in Shirdi at an early age and disappears. He goes to the Himalayas and returns after a gap of 9 years. He chooses a dilapidated mosque as his abode. Amazed by his presence and miracles, the local people start calling him Sai.

page113.title: Villagelo Vinayakudu
page113.description: The film is a sequel to the 2008 hit, Vinayakudu. The movie is about how Krishnudu, a teacher by profession wins the heart of Lakshmipati,  father of Kavya, whom he is in love with.

page113.title: Vaana
page113.description: A remake of Kannada language Blockbuster film Mungaru Male.Abhiram is the only son of his parents. On a visit to a mall amidst a heavy wind, he spots a pretty girl, Nandini. Whilst staring at her, he inadvertently falls into a manhole.

page113.title: Sundarakanda
page113.description: Pinky is the daughter of Sita, who keeps away from her husband. On Pinky's insistence, Sita reveals the past. She met Raja Ravivarma, son of Zamindar Surendra Varma on a study tour of a tribal village. They fell in love and got married then and there.

page114.title: Pravarakhyudu
page114.description: Sasi (Jagapathi Babu), a professor of biology at Harvard University of the US, makes a comeback to his native place. He makes an attempt to settle in life for which he prompts a couple of alliances. But, they don't fit into his mindset.

page114.title: Aa Okkadu
page114.description: Sri Krishna is a successful criminal lawyer. Bujji works under Sri Krishna. Dr. Pavitra is a psychiatrist who works in a mental hospital.Sri Krishna and Pavitra are disciples of a godman.  Slowly a few people associated with Pavitra are killed.

page114.title: Josh
page114.description: Satya (Naga Chaitanya) is a student who discontinues his college in Vizag and comes to Hyderabad to stay with his uncle (Sunil). He sees JD (JD Chakri), a small-time politician manipulating two student gangs in a college to serve his interests.

page114.title: Jaganmohini
page114.description: It is a remake of the B. Vittalacharya cult horror film of the same name. A Telugu Dubbed Version.The movie begins at Pachai Theevu, ruled by a mighty king. His son is a valourous youth who sets out on a mission to capture pirates in the sea.

page114.title: Arya 2
page114.description: An unstable and unpredictable guy causes havoc for his 'best friend' and lover.Arya 2 is a sequel of blockbuster movie Arya. It is a romantic comedy entertainer. In which, Allu Arjun is playing the role of a software engineer in this movie.

page114.title: Manorama
page114.description: The story begins with Gitanjali a k a Gilli (Charmy Kaur) who comes to Hyderabad to spend a few days with her friends (Lahari and Sridhar). She lives near Manorama café and there comes a stranger (Nishan) with a bag. A thriller not to be missed!!

page115.title: Posani Gentleman
page115.description: Posani Gentleman is a message oriented movie with comedy backdrop. In which Posani murali Krishna playing a role of software Engg and Aarthi Agarwal paring up for the first time with Posani in this movie.

page115.title: Satruvu
page115.description: Anu is the daughter of the city' mayor and heir to a fortune running into thousands of crores. Some unidentified killers hatch a plan to kill her but are saved by Shankaranna, a small-time conman. She appoints Shankar as her bodyguard to protect her.

page115.title: Routine Love Story
page115.description: Sanju (Sundeep Kishan) is a college going student who falls for a girl Tanvi (Regina Cassandra) at first sight. They get along over a period of time but unsure of the advancing in their relationship because another person might not be perfect.

page115.title: Devaraja
page115.description: Dorababu lives in a village in Godavari district and he has a gang of friends.His daily life is all about cards, drinks, women and has a carefree attitude. He comes across Swapna who comes new to the village and due to certain incidents she falls in love with him.

page115.title: Yamudu
page115.description: Surya plays a cop in Singam, a film that revolves around smuggling activities in Rameshwaram and is on a mission to apprehend a local M.L.A. (Telugu Dubbed Version of 2010 Tamil Movie Singam)

page115.title: Seetharamula Kalyanam Lankalo
page115.description: A woman is abducted by a man who wants to forcibly wed her. Seeta Ramula Kalyanam is a 2010 Telugu action drama film, directed by Eeshwar starring Nitin and Hansika Motwani.

page116.title: Maryada Ramanna
page116.description: A man returns to his parents' village to claim his land. Along the way, he befriends a charming young woman. Unbeknownst to him, her family has a long-standing feud with his family.

page116.title: Jhummandi Naadam
page116.description: Balu has only one mission in his life - to become a great playback singer like SP Balasubramanyam. He challenges a landlord in his village and comes to Hyderabad to become a singer.

page116.title: Darling (telugu)
page116.description: To save himself from an unwanted marriage to a gangster's daughter, a man tells the story of reuniting with his childhood sweetheart in Switzerland.

page116.title: Ye Maaya Chesave
page116.description: The movie portrays the complicated relationship between Karthik and Jessie whom he falls in love with. Jessie is torn between her love for Karthik and her family, who is steadfast in their disapproval of him.

page116.title: Mayabazar
page116.description: The story revolves around the characters in the Hindu Epic "The Mahabharata" and is set in Dwaraka, the hometown of Lord Krishna (NTR).This is the digitally remastered and colorized version that was released on 30th January 2010

page116.title: Masth
page116.description: The aspiring model Shivaji loses his sight after prolonged exposure to the photo studio's light, while one more aspiring singer Srinivas becomes mute after a cacophonous humming

page117.title: Maro Charitra
page117.description: Balu falls in love with Swapna at first sight, but their parents oppose the match and suggest they wait a year to see if they are truly in love.

page117.title: Kalyanram Kathi
page117.description: The protagonist aspires to become a football player but ends up as a goon in the Rayalaseema region to protect the interests of his married sister.

page117.title: Eenadu
page117.description: A remake of the 2008 Hindi film A Wednesday!.A common man tries to fight terrorism by making anonymous calls to cops. Will he succeed?

page117.title: Bendu Apparao RMP
page117.description: Bendu Appa Rao is a RMP doctor in a tiny village in East Godavari. Though he does not have much knowledge about medicines, he uses his brain to come out of critical situations. He earns money by all means to help his sister.

page117.title: Vachadu Gellichadu
page117.description: Telugu Dubbed version of 2011 Tamil movie Vandhaan Vendraan.Arjun's girlfriend will marry him if he convinces a suave don to surrender to the police.

page117.title: Solo: Solid Love Story
page117.description: Gautham is an orphan who always wishes to get married to a girl from a joint family to experience the love of relationships and elders. He falls in love with Vaishnavi who belongs to a joint family.

page118.title: Sneha Geetham
page118.description: The story is about three young guys Ravi, Krishna and Arjun who are engineering graduates wanting to be an entrepreneur, a software employee and a film director respectively. They fall in love with Shailu, Pooja and Maha respectively.

page118.title: Veer (telugu)
page118.description: A Pindari prince (Salman Khan) goes to England to study military tactics so that he can avenge his people, but while there, he falls in love.An Epic Love Story Of A Warrior!! (Telugu Dubbed)

page118.title: Quick Gun Murugun
page118.description: A once-dead vegetarian cowboy is sent back to life to battle a beef-eating villain.A spoof on Indian western movies, featuring songs, melodrama and action sequences including a duel in a traffic jam.

page118.title: Prasthanam
page118.description: Prasthanam is a poetic and intense character drama enacted by Sharwanand, Sai Kumar, and Sundeep Kishan. The movie is set in Vijayawada with a contemporary political backdrop.

page118.title: Kedi
page118.description: Rummy agrees to marry Janki, but not until he has accumulated a substantial wealth, so he decides to become a gambler.

page118.title: Kalavar King
page118.description: A village boy aspires to get ahead in life easily, for this he ends up taking up loans from everyone. He falls in love with a girl and mends his way of life, becomes a loan recovery agent.

page119.title: Ganesh
page119.description: Ganesh is an orphan who always pitches in to help needy people. In one such strange situation, he is forced to pretend to Divya that he loves her. But later on, she comes to know that he is loving her to fulfill some other ambition.

page119.title: Aawara
page119.description: An engineering graduate is not serious about his job or his future even when his friends advise him about life. He falls in love with a girl he saw at a bus stop and finally gets to ride with her in a car.(Telugu Dubbed Version of Paiyya Tamil movie)

page119.title: Life Style
page119.description: Life Style is a drama based movie in which the story is about five youths who studied together in the same college. The main story is about how they have maintained their friendship after the graduation also.

page119.title: Fitting Master
page119.description: A woman falls for a man she once hated, after she is rescued by him. She later learns of his dark side and confronts him, after which the man reveals details about his life and his motives.

page119.title: Bommarillu
page119.description: A young man realizes that he has to push back against his domineering father if he wants to find true happiness and love.

page119.title: Virodhi
page119.description: Political journalist Jayadev unearths several scams made by a politician who in turn invites him to bribe him. He refuses to relent, and as they discuss, a group of Naxals attack the politician and kill him off and Jayadev is held as their hostage.

page120.title: Nuvva Nena
page120.description: Avinash is a small time crook who creates havoc in the town along with his friend Ali. After a big robbery, they escape to Hyderabad along with 60 lakhs in cash. Unexpectedly, Avinash comes across the gorgeous Dr. Nandini, and falls in love.

page120.title: Racha
page120.description: Raju makes his living by betting. He lives with his adopted parents who support his means of living. Everything goes on as usual until tragedy strikes the family in the form of his father who is diagnosed with cirrhosis as a result of heavy drinking.

page120.title: Pilla Zamindar
page120.description: PJ has to go through a rough journey of living like a common man and graduating from a village-based college to inherit his grandfather's wealth.

page120.title: Parugu
page120.description: A group of friends is brought forcefully to a village, where they are asked to help find the daughter of the village head, who believes these friends have helped in the eloping of his daughter with her love interest.

page120.title: Panjaa
page120.description: Jai (Pawan), an orphan, is taken in and nurtured into a hard hitting gangster by Bhagwan (Jackie Shroff). When not busy kicking the hell out of rival gangs, he escapes his lovelorn life by running a nursery with his pal Chotu (Ali).

page120.title: Oosaravelli
page120.description: Tony is a wily youngster who does illegal things for money. He falls in love with Niharika during a freak incident. He keeps following her and proposing to her. But she is engaged to some other rich guy. But, Tony has a secret mission.

professionals.name: N. T. Rama Rao Jr. T

page121.title: Oh My Friend
page121.description: In this story about love and friendship, Chandu (Siddharth) and Siri (Shruti) are childhood buddies, who grow up sharing their lives together. While Chandu wants to become a musician, Siri aims to be a classical dancer.

page121.title: Nippu
page121.description: The story begins with Surya who owns a gym centre and he also has a good friend Sriram. Surya is in love with his friend’s sister Meghna and after some cat and mouse games, she also falls in love.

page121.title: Mogudu
page121.description: A couple truly in love get married. On the day of marriage just after the ritual due to a stupid reason an argument sparks, the egoes crash which turns into violence. The couple separates. How they finally unite is rest of the movie.

page121.title: Life Is Beautiful
page121.description: It is a coming of age story of six youngsters, set in the beautiful nostalgic world of a working-middle class neighborhood.

page121.title: Koffi Bar
page121.description: Koffi Bar is about the way life changes to a couple of youngsters who by accident get to know some terror plans of terrorists in a coffee bar. This knowledge added with some romance lead them to a horrifying experience.

page121.title: Julayi
page121.description: Bittu is a notorious bank robber who embezzles 15 billion in a daring bank heist. He runs into an unlikely nemesis. An enraged Bittu swears revenge.

page122.title: Gabbar Singh
page122.description: A boy runs away from home, angry with his stepfather and half-brother. Years later, he becomes a police inspector and fights a notorious criminal.

page122.title: English Vinglis (telugu)
page122.description: A quiet, sweet tempered housewife endures small slights from her well-educated husband and daughter every day because of her inability to speak and understand English. (Telugu Dubbed Version)

page122.title: Rebel
page122.description: Rishi (Prabhas) is out to get his father's killers. But to get at them he first needs to befriend Nandini (Tamannaah,) a 'hip-hop dancer' based in Bangkok. And Rishi will not stop at anything to get his revenge.

page122.title: Dammu
page122.description: An orphan gets adopted by a rich and powerful family looking for an heir. But the family has a dark violent past due to dispute with other rival family. What will he do when the fate of his village depends on him?

page122.title: Cameraman Gangatho Rambabu
page122.description: Rambabu (Pawan Kalyan) owns a garage and is a mechanic. But he is a different young man who is sensitive to injustice and doesn't hesitate to take action as a responsible citizen.  A political action blockbuster!!

page122.title: Badrinath
page122.description: Badri, a warrior and the protector of Badrinath temple, tries to revive Alakananda's faith in God, thus leading to battles between him and her cruel uncle, Sarkaar.
